title: Ukraine forces destroy Russian column with Corsar guided missile launcher
description: Ukrainian Guardsman blasts a Russian armoured vehicle with a Corsar guided missile launcher from a distance of 1.5 miles.|The Centre for Strategic Communications (StratCom) said on 6th June: â€œWith each shot, the Ukrainian defender reduces the enemy equipment!|â€œThis is the work of a National Guardsman with the call sign â€˜Hulkâ€™ in Donbas. The warrior owns the Corsar system and neutralised enemy equipment from a distance of 2.5 kilometres (1.55 miles)!â€|SratCom added: â€œReal superheroes are defending Ukraine!â€|In the footage, â€˜Hulkâ€™ is seen shooting a missile from the launcher before apparently hitting an enemy armoured vehicle travelling along the road. By the end of the clip, the whole convoy has been destroyed.|Russian troops invaded Ukraine on 24th February in what the Kremlin is still calling a "special military operation". Today marks the 104th day of the campaign.|From 24th February to 6th June, the total combat losses of Russian troops stand at around 31,250 personnel, according to the General Staff of the Armed Forces of Ukraine.|The Ukrainian military also claims that Russia has lost 1,386 tanks, 3,400 armoured fighting vehicles, 690 artillery systems, 207 multiple launch rocket systems, 96 anti-aircraft systems, 211 warplanes, 176 helicopters, 2,395 motor vehicles and fuel tankers, 13 vessels, 551 unmanned aerial vehicles, 53 units of special equipment, and 125 cruise missiles.|Meanwhile, the Ukrainian Centre for Strategic Communications (StratCom) claimed on 6th June that Russian Major General Roman Kutuzov was killed in a battle near Popasna in the Luhansk region.|StratCom said: â€œExclusive. title: Presiden Jokowi Menerima Menlu Arab Saudi, Istana Merdeka, 7 Juni 2022
description: *Presiden Jokowi Terima Kunjungan Menlu Arab Saudi, Bahas Soal Haji hingga Ekonomi*|Presiden Joko Widodo menerima kunjungan kehormatan Menteri Luar Negeri (Menlu) Kerajaan Arab Saudi, Pangeran Faisal Bin Farhan Al Saud, di Istana Merdeka, Jakarta, pada Selasa, 7 Juni 2022. Dalam pertemuan tersebut, Presiden Jokowi dan Menlu Arab Saudi membahas berbagai hal, mulai dari soal kepentingan umat hingga soal ekonomi.|"Pertama-tama Bapak Presiden berbicara mengenai masalah kepentingan umat yang dalam hal ini adalah pelaksanaan ibadah haji. Bapak Presiden mengatakan apresiasi terhadap pelaksanaan haji tahun ini setelah karena pandemi dua tahun tidak dilakukan pelaksanaan haji, dan Indonesia mendapatkan kuota terbesar lebih dari 100 ribu, tepatnya adalah 100.051 orang," ujar Menteri Luar Negeri Retno Marsudi yang turut dalam pertemuan. |"Dengan membaiknya situasi pandemi, tentunya harapan kita semua umat Islam seluruh dunia adalah di masa mendatang kuota ini akan terus ditingkatkan dan Presiden mendoakan pelaksanaan haji tahun ini dapat berjalan lancar dan aman," lanjutnya.|Sementara itu, Menlu Arab Saudi menjelaskan mengenai rencana ke depan, yakni apabila situasi membaik kuota haji akan ditingkatkan. Selain itu, pemerintah Arab Saudi juga akan terus membangun fasilitas-fasilitas untuk mendukung pelaksanaan ibadah haji.|Kedua, Presiden Jokowi menyampaikan rencana Indonesia untuk membangun Indonesian House di Kota Makkah, untuk memberikan dukungan yang maksimal kepada para jamaah umrah dan haji Indonesia. "Kita minta dukungan dari otoritas pemerintah, dari Saudi, dan pesan ini akan disampaikan oleh Menlu Saudi kepada otoritas di Saudi Arabia," imbuhnya.|Ketiga mengenai hubungan antarmasyarakat, Menlu Retno melaporkan kepada Presiden Jokowi bahwa otoritas Arab Saudi telah mencabut larangan warganya untuk berkunjung ke Indonesia. Menurut Menlu, hal tersebut merupakan hasil dari pembicaraan yang sudah lama antara pihak Indonesia dengan pihak Arab Saudi, mencakup data-data mengenai kondisi Covid-19 di Indonesia yang terus mendapatkan apresiasi dari dunia.|"Saya sampaikan dalam pembicaraan saya sebelumnya dengan otoritas Saudi antara lain bahwa baru-baru ini Indonesia di Bali menjadi tuan rumah salah satu perhelatan _in person_. Jadi secara fisik datang pertemuan PBB yang dihadiri oleh lebih dari lima ribu orang dan alhamdulillah setelah pertemuan kita tidak mendengar ada laporan yang siginifikan mengenai dampak Covidnya terhadap para peserta," jelasnya. |"PBB sendiri memberikan apresiasi terhadap Indonesia, bagaimana Indonesia mengelola Covid, dan kemarin kita tahu juga Perdana Menteri Australia memberikan apresiasi yang sama. Jadi sekali lagi kita sambut baik keputusan otoritas Saudi untuk mencabut larangan warganya untuk berkunjung ke Indonesia yang kita harapkan akan berdampak pada pariwisata dan juga kunjungan-kunjungan bisnis," tambahnya.|Terakhir, Presiden Jokowi berbicara mengenai ekonomi dan menyampaikan harapannya bahwa apa yang telah dibahas dapat diimplementasikan secara konkret. Salah satu rencana kerja sama ekonomi yang terus dibahas antara lain di bidang transisi energi.|"Di dalam pembicaraan tadi Menteri Luar Negeri Saudi Arabia menyampaikan pesan dari raja dan dari putra mahkota bahwa Indonesia adalah salah satu priotitas paling tinggi Saudi Arabia untuk melakukan kerja sama ekonomi," tandas Menlu Retno.|Dalam pertemuan tersebut, Presiden Jokowi turut didampingi juga oleh Sekretaris Kabinet Pramono Anung. Sementara itu, Menlu Arab Saudi didampingi oleh Duta Besar Kerajaan Arab Saudi untuk Republik Indonesia Esam A. Abid Althagafi.|Jakarta, 7 Juni 2022|Biro Pers, Media, dan Informasi Sekretariat Presiden|Website: https://www.presidenri.go.id|YouTube: Sekretariat Presiden

title: Cukup 10 Menit! Resep BAKSO KEPITING SAUS SINGAPORE [Chili Crab Stick]
description: Resep lengkap buka di description box ini dan geser sampai ke bawah.|**English description is at the bottom section.**|00:00 : intro|01:00 : persiapan bahan (prepping the ingredients)|01:47 : potong bahan-bahan (slicing the ingredients)|02:29 : goreng crab stick (frying the crab sticks)|03:10 : mulai memasak (start cooking)|04:42 : hidangan siap dan serving (the dish is ready to serve)|#ResepChiliCrabStick #ResepCrabStick #ResepDevinaHermawan|===================|Resep Chili Crab Stick (untuk 2 porsi)|Bahan:|12 pcs crab stick|2 sdt bumbu gulai instan|1 butir telur|1,5 sdm saus tiram|2 sdm saus sambal|300 ml air|1,5 sdm maizena|Â½ buah bawang bombai|2 siung bawang putih|2 buah cabai merah|4 buah cabai rawit|1-2 sdt gula pasir|Â½ sdt kaldu bubuk / penyedap|Minyak goreng secukupnya|Pelengkap:|Nais putih|Langkah:|1. Potong bawang bombai, bawang putih, cabai merah, dan cabai rawit merah|2. Belah dua crab stick kemudian panaskan sedikit minyak, goreng hingga kering, sisihkan |3. Sisihkan sebagian minyak lalu tumis bawang bombai, aduk rata|4. Masukkan bawang putih, aduk rata kemudian masukkan cabai merah dan cabai rawit, tumis hingga wangi|5. Masukkan bumbu gulai, saus tiram, saus sambal, gula, dan penyedap, aduk rata|6. Campurkan maizena dengan air lalu tuang ke dalam wajan, aduk hingga mengental|7. Kocok lepas telur, tuang ke dalam wajan perlahan sambil diaduk|8. Masukkan crab stick, masak sesaat|9. Chili crab stick siap disajikan |===================|[ENGLISH]|Chili Crab Stick Recipe (yield 2 servings)|Ingredients:|12 pc crab stick|2 tsp instant Gulai paste|1 pc egg|1.5 tbsp oyster sauce|2 tbsp chili sauce|300 ml water|1.5 tbsp cornstarch|Â½ pc onion|2 clove garlic|2 pc red chili|4 pc Thai chili|1-2 tsp sugar|Â½ tsp stock powder / MSG|Oil, as needed|Others:|Rice|Steps:|1. Slice the onion, garlic, red chili, and red Thai chili.|2. Halve the crab sticks. Heat some oil and fry them until crisp. Set aside.|3. Set aside some of the oil, then sautÃ© the onion.|4. Add garlic. Stir, then add red chili and Thai chili. SautÃ© until fragrant.|5. Add the Gulai paste, oyster sauce, chili sauce, sugar, and MSG. Stir well.|6. Mix the cornstarch with water and add it into the pan. Stir until the sauce thickens.|7. Lightly beat the egg. Pour into the pan slowly while stirring.|8. Add the crab sticks in and cook for a moment.|9. Chili Crab Stick is ready to serve.|===================|Official Site:|https://devinahermawan.com/|Instagram:|https://instagram.com/devinahermawan/ |Business inquiries: contact@devinahermawan.com|Donâ€™t reupload our content but you can share our videos. title: J&K: Lashkar terrorist from Pakistan among 2 killed in Kupwara, another shot down in Sopore
description: In a major win for security forces in Jammu and Kashmir, 2 Lashkar terrorists were gunned down in a fierce encounter in Kupwara. Police clarified that one of the terrorists was identified as Tufail. He was a Pakistani national. The encounter broke out in early hours of the day in the Chaktaras Kandi area of the district. This comes a day after, another LeT (Lashkar-e-Taiba) terrorist was killed in an encounter in the Sopore town of Baramulla district. As per the documents recovered from the Pakistani terrorist, his name was Hanzalla and he was a resident of Lahore. Watch this video for more information.|#pakistan #lashkar #terrorist #indianforces #jammuandkashmir #sopore #kupwara #baramulla #let #jkpolice

title: 'Biggest threat to...': Elon Musk cautions about population collapse in China | Details
description: Elon Musk has yet again raised an alarm on Twitter over the population issue. In his latest tweet, Musk cautions about a possible 'population collapse' that the world may see in the near future. The tech billionaire has been voicing his opinion on the matter for quite some time now. This time, he took China's example to bolster his argument while responding to an article by BBC. Last month, too he had stressed that 'population collapse is the biggest threat to the civilisation.' The 50-year-old billionaire has been strongly opposing the rising trend of keeping the birth rate low. Watch this report to know more.|#elonmusk #china #chinachildpolicy #population #threat #tesla #elon #birthrate #globalnews #globaltimes #elonmuskquote

title: Rechter leest berichten opdrachtgever moord Peter R. de Vries voor
description: Tijdens de eerste dag van de inhoudelijke behandeling van de rechtszaak over de moord op Peter R. de Vries las de rechter vanmorgen berichten die over de moord zouden gaan voor. |Het ging om een chatgesprek op een Google Pixel-telefoon, die telefoon lag in de auto  waarin de twee opgepakt werden. Een deel van het gesprek was in het Pools en een deel in het Nederlands. "En een deel van het gesprek zou kunnen passen bij de gebeurtenissen die die middag en avond van 6 juli hebben plaatsgevonden", zei de rechter. |Zo stond er in het chatgesprek 'daar moet je hem doen'. "Leeg die ding op hem", las de rechter voor. "Daar heb je Glock." En dan, een minuut later, van de Google Pixel-telefoon naar de andere telefoon: 'Komt goes, geen stress'. U hoort mij komt goes zeggen, zo staat het ook in het gesprek en ik probeer zoveel mogelijk het bericht aan te houden."|Om 16.58 uur werden er nog twee foto's van Peter R. de Vries gestuurd, met als tekst, 'deze hond moet je hebben'. "Si", antwoordde degene op de Google Pixel-telefoon. Om 17.00 uur volgde er nog een bericht van de andere telefoon: 'Knal op zijn hoofd'. Vanaf de Google Pixel-telefoon werd bevestigend geantwoord: 'Ja man, kk hard'. |Delano G. beriep zich op zijn zwijgrecht. Kamil E. zei dat hij de telefoon niet eens in zijn handen had gehad. Op de telefoon is wel volgens de hoogste waarschijnlijkheid dna-materiaal van G. gevonden. |De twee mannen die verdacht worden van (betrokkenheid bij) de dodelijke aanslag op Peter R. de Vries, staan vandaag voor voor de rechter. Het gaat om de 22-jarige Delano G. en Kamil E., een Pool van 35 jaar. Tijdens de zitting wordt de zaak voor het eerst inhoudelijk behandeld. Naar verwachting komt het Openbaar Ministerie vandaag met een strafeis voor de moord op Peter R. de Vries.|De Vries werd op 6 juli vorig jaar neergeschoten in de Lange Leidsedwarsstraat, kort nadat hij bij een live-uitzending van RTL Boulevard was geweest. De twee verdachten werden nog diezelfde avond door de politie opgepakt. Delano G. wordt vanaf dat moment gezien als de vermoedelijke schutter, Kamil E. zou de bestuurder van de vluchtauto zijn geweest. De Vries overleed negen dagen na de aanslag.|Voor de zitting van vandaag zijn er al drie zogenoemde pro forma-zittingen geweest. Hoewel er toen niet inhoudelijk op de zaak is ingegaan, kwamen er wel al meerdere details rond de spraakmakende moordzaak naar buiten.|Zo zou G. met een omgebouwd alarmpistool vier keer op De Vries hebben geschoten. En E. zou op zijn beurt nog een voorverkenning hebben gedaan bij de parkeergarage in de Lange Leidsedwarsstraat. Ook zijn de twee voorafgaand aan de moord nog op camerabeelden te zien in de nabijheid van de redactie van RTL Boulevard.|Waar Delano G. zijn kaken tijdens de pro forma-zittingen telkens stijf op elkaar hield, liet Kamil E. zich wel een aantal keer horen. "Ik heb niemand doodgemaakt, ik wist niks van de moord en ik heb geen wapen gezienâ€, aldus E., die verklaarde ingehuurd te zijn voor een klus waarvan hij de inhoud niet wist. Tijdens de tweede regiezitting zei hij niet de man te zijn die met G. op de camerabeelden te zien is. â€œIk was bij mijn moeder.â€|De meest indringende details moeten op dat moment nog komen. Tijdens de derde pro forma-zitting, op 3 maart van dit jaar, blijkt dat de politie in de vluchtauto een Google Pixel 3 heeft gevonden. In dat telefoontje is een chatgesprek te lezen waar Delano G., Kamil E. en een derde persoon (aangeduid met codenaam NN-*4229) deelnemer van zijn.|âŒ|âŒ|âŒ|AT5 - Echt Amsterdams Nieuws|Abonneer hier op ons youtubekanaal: |https://www.youtube.com/AT5|Tips of opmerkingen?|Whatsapp: 06 511 909 38|Telefoon: 020 555 1155|Volg AT5:|www.at5.nl |Instagram: instagram.com/at5.nl|Facebook: facebook.com/at5nl|Twitter: twitter.com/at5

title: Pimpinan Khilafatul Muslimin Ditangkap, Ini Tanggapan Walikota Bandar Lampung!
description: KOMPAS.TV, LAMPUNG  Walikota Eva Dwiana tidak menyangka soal penangkapan kholifah atau Pimpinan Pusat Khilafatul Muslimin Abdul Qadir Hasan Baraja di Bandar Lampung pada Selasa (7/6/2022) pagi ini.||||Pasalnya, keberadaan Khilafatul Muslimin yang aktivitas keseharianya lekat dengan kegiatan keagamaan, justru dinilai polisi telah menyebarkan paham atau ideologi yang bertentangan dengan Pancasila dan NKRI.||||Baca Juga Jamaah Khilafatul Muslimin Kecewa Pemimpinnya Ditangkap di https://www.kompas.tv/article/296580/jamaah-khilafatul-muslimin-kecewa-pemimpinnya-ditangkap||||Merespons hal itu, Eva menggandeng MUI, FKUB, NU, TNI-POLRI untuk mencegah paham anti-Pancasila ini menyebar di Kota Bandar Lampung.||||Bahkan, ia juga akan melakukan pembinaan pada pondok-pondok pesantren dan juga lingkungan pendidikan lainnya untuk terus menyosialisasikan ideologi Pancasila.||||"Pertama, Bunda kaget karena ada penangkapan di Bandar Lampung. Tapi, kami bersyukur dan akan antisipasi kecamatan/kelurahan yang ada di Bandar Lampung," kata Eva.||||Baca Juga Pimpinan Pusat Khilafatul Muslimin Diamankan Polisi di https://www.kompas.tv/article/296547/pimpinan-pusat-khilafatul-muslimin-diamankan-polisi||||Kini, Abdul Qadir Hasan Baraja langsung di bawa ke Mapolresta Bandar Lampung yang nantinya akan diberangkatkan ke Mapolda Metro Jaya, Jakarta.||||#khilafatulmuslimin #penangkapan #abdulqadirhasanbaraja||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296592/pimpinan-khilafatul-muslimin-ditangkap-ini-tanggapan-walikota-bandar-lampung

title: Jamaah Khilafatul Muslimin Kecewa Pemimpinnya Ditangkap
description: KOMPAS.TV, LAMPUNG  Puluhan anggota kelompok Khilafatul Muslimin menyampaikan kekecewaannya usai penangkapan Abdul Qadir Hasan Baraja, Selasa (7/6/2022) hari ini.||||Penangkapan tersebut dinilai tidak pantas lantaran dilakukan saat sedang beribadah di dalam masjid kekhalifaan yang berada di Jalan WR Supratman, Bumi Waras, Teluk Betung, Bandar Lampung.||||Baca Juga Pimpinan Pusat Khilafatul Muslimin Diamankan Polisi di https://www.kompas.tv/article/296547/pimpinan-pusat-khilafatul-muslimin-diamankan-polisi||||Abu Bakar selaku Pemimpin Khilafatul Muslimin Wilayah Kota Bandar Lampung bahkan menyebut, kegiatan konvoi syiar keagamaan yang dilakukan di sejumlah wilayah termasuk Berebes, Jawa Tengah merupakan program wewenang setiap wilayah yang tidak ada kaitannya dengan Abdul Qadir Hasan Baraja.||||Dirinya juga menambahkan, usai kholifah dibawa ke Polda Metro Jaya, nantinya akan ada anggota Khilafatul Muslimin di daerah jawa yang akan melakukan pendampingan.||||"Aneh aja gitu, loh. Orang solat ditangkep. Sementara, Khilafatul Muslimin ini tidak berbuat apa-apa. Adapun konvoi motor itu kan gak nabrak orang. Kok, jadi aneh. Apa apa dengan negeri ini? Kok, jadi anti sama Islam," ungkap Abu Bakar.||||Baca Juga Kholifah Khilafatul Muslimin Bantah anti-Pancasila dan NKRI di https://www.kompas.tv/article/294919/kholifah-khilafatul-muslimin-bantah-anti-pancasila-dan-nkri||||Selain melakukan penangkapan, polisi juga mengamankan sejumlah barang bukti, di antaranya perangkat komputer, pakaian keanggotaan, serta bukti buku bacaan dari hasil penggeledahan.||||#khilafatulmuslimin #penangkapan #abdulqadirhasanbaraja||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296580/jamaah-khilafatul-muslimin-kecewa-pemimpinnya-ditangkap

title: Momen Anies Baswedan Temui Ridwan Kamil, Sampaikan Doa Untuk Eril
description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS.TV  Sejumlah Pejabat bertakziah ke Gubernur Jawa Barat, Ridwan Kamil, seperti hal nya juga Gubernur DKI Jakarta Anies Baswedan bertakziah ke Gedung Pakuan Bandung pada Senin (6/6) temui Ridwan Kamil.||||Kedatangan Anies beserta istri untuk mendokan keluarga Ridwan Kamil yang ditinggal putra sulung mereka, Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz..||||Atas kejadian yang menimpa Ridwan Kamil dan keluarga, Anies mendoakan agar kebaikan Eril semasa hidup dapat menjadi pembuka pintu surga bagi kedua orang tuanya.||||Baca Juga Adam Deni Kembali ke Ruang Sidang Usai Dituntut 8 Tahun Penjara, Pembelaannya akan Dibacakan di https://www.kompas.tv/article/296430/adam-deni-kembali-ke-ruang-sidang-usai-dituntut-8-tahun-penjara-pembelaannya-akan-dibacakan||||Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril dinyatakan meninggal dunia usai hilang dan hanyut di sungai Aare, Swiss.||||Hingga kini proses pencarian Eril masih dilakukan. Namun usai tujuh hari sejak hilang, keluarga meyakini Eril meninggal dunia karena tenggelam.||||Video Editor: Febi||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296446/momen-anies-baswedan-temui-ridwan-kamil-sampaikan-doa-untuk-eril

title: How an unfazed India is talking to Russia to double the oil imports despite West's criticism
description: As Moscow is offering deep discounts on its crude oil amid its boycott by the U.S & EU due to its invasion of Ukraine, India is looking at purchasing more low-cost Russian oil from Rosneft PJSC, according to a Bloomberg report. These deals, if closed, will be over and above the purchases, India already made through other deals. India imports over 80 percent of its crude oil requirements. The country imported 193.5 million tonnes of crude oil in the current financial year till February, at a cost of $105.8 billion. The crude oil in the country mainly comes from the Middle East and the US. From Russia, in the whole year 2021, the country bought just 12 million barrels of oil, which is only 2 percent of its total imports. Indiaâ€™s own domestic production is more than that. However, the Biden administration has been pressurising to end deals with Russia but India remains unfazed. title: Eksklusif! Detik-detik Penangkapan Abdul Qadir Baraja Pimpinan Khalifatul Muslimin di Lampung
description: LAMPUNG, KOMPAS TV - Polisi menangkap pimpinan Khalifatul Muslimin Abdul Qadir Baraja di Lampung, Selasa (7/6).||||Penangkapan berlangsung di kediaman Abdul Qodir Baraja yang juga satu tempat dengan kantor pusat Khalifatul Muslimin di Teluk Betung, Sukaraja, Bandar Lampung.||||Abdul Qadir Baraja kemudian dibawa ke Polresta Bandar Lampung.||||Baca Juga Abdul Qadir Baraja Ditangkap, NII : Saya Tidak Kaget, Mereka Bahkan Ingin Buat Pemerintahan Sendiri di https://www.kompas.tv/article/296387/abdul-qadir-baraja-ditangkap-nii-saya-tidak-kaget-mereka-bahkan-ingin-buat-pemerintahan-sendiri||||Penangkapan dilakukan oleh tim dari Polda Metro Jaya dibantu oleh petugas dari Polresta Bandar Lampung.||||Penangkapan Abdul Qadir Baraja terjadi usai polisi tetapkan tiga tersangka di Brebes atas kasus konvoi 'kebangkitan khilafah'.||||Polres Kabupaten Brebes tetapkan tiga orang tersangka atas kasus konvoi kebangkita khilafah yang dilakukan kelompok Khilafatul Muslimin.||||Penetapan tersangka merupakan hasil dari serangkaian penyidikan. ||Ketiga tersangka bertanggung jawab atas kegiatan konvoi kebangkitan khilafah yang sempat viral.||||Kapolres sebut meodus operasi para tersangka adalah membagikan maklumat pada masyarakat tentang kebangkita khilafah.||||Baca Juga Situasi TKP Penangkapan Abdul Qadir Baraja, Pimpinan Khilafatul Muslimin di Bandar Lampung! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/296385/situasi-tkp-penangkapan-abdul-qadir-baraja-pimpinan-khilafatul-muslimin-di-bandar-lampung||||Kegiatan tersebut dinilai meresahkan warga, termasuk kegiatan konvoi yang belum lama ini viral.||||"Menyebarkan berita bohong di tengah masyarakat, sehingga menyebabkan keonaran. Jadi, dari kegiatan-kegiatan Khilafatul Muslimin seperti konvoi, pembagian maklumat, membuat masyarakat Brebes merasa resah," ujar AKBP Fasisal Febrianto selaku Kapolres Brebes.||||Video Editor: Laurensius Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296402/eksklusif-detik-detik-penangkapan-abdul-qadir-baraja-pimpinan-khalifatul-muslimin-di-lampung

title: 'Tumors just vanished': Cancer patients now in remission after drug trial

title: China, Pak in target range, India successfully test-fires nuclear-capable Agni-IV missile
description: A nuclear-capable Agni-IV ballistic missile was successfully test-fired off the Odisha coast today. The ballistic missile is capable of striking targets 4,000 km away. The defence ministry said the missile was test-fired off APJ Abdul Kalam Island in Odisha. It said the successful test reaffirms India's policy of having a "credible minimum deterrence" capability. Agni-IV is the fourth in the Agni series of missiles developed by the DRDO. Last year, India successfully test-fired nuclear capable strategic Agni Prime missile. Watch the full video for more.|#Agni-IV #Agni-4 #NuclearCapableMissile #DRDO #India #China #Pakistan #Missile #missilelaunch #kalamisland #defenceministry

title: Toyota GR Supra 2023 | Cambio MANUALE (!!!) 340 CV e -40 kg!
description: La aspettavano tutti ed ora finalmente Ã¨ arrivata! Parliamo della Toyota GR Supra 2023 con il nuovo cambio manuale a sei marce. Una piccola grande rivoluzione, il sacro graal per gli appassionati di auto GT ad alte prestazioni old-school che arriverÃ  presto nelle concessionarie dei marchi abilitati alla vendita del marchio Gazoo Racing...anche in Europa! Una combinazione folle, a suo modo dÃ©modÃ©, ma assolutamente in grado di scaldare il cuore di tutti quegli appassionati che nella Supra, sino ad oggi, ci avevano visto troppa BMW e poco giappone. Del resto la comunanza di progetto con BMW Z4 Ã¨ evidente - ed in Giappone non fanno nemmeno troppo per celarla - e la perfezione di quell'automatico ZF8 abbinato all'allungo infinito del sei cilindri in linea sovralimentato avevano certamente il gusto della birra piuttosto che di quel sakÃ¨ che i cultori hanno cercato - e mai trovato - nella Supra A90.|Distinguerla dalla â€œnormaleâ€ Supra Ã¨ relativamente semplice: basta guardare il colore della scritta - ora Ã¨ rossa - e dare unâ€™occhiata agli interni dove la leva del cambio manuale, lâ€™aggiunta del pedale della frizione e il nuovo disegno del tunnel centrale - con il riposizionamento dellâ€™i-drive per il controllo del nuovo sistema multimediale - fanno la differenza con la Supra che abbiamo conosciuto sino ad oggi.|Sotto al cofano il B58 Ã¨ sempre il solito pezzo di motore che abbiamo conosciuto su Supra e su altre decine di prodotti BMW mentre il cambio manuale porta con se anche una rapportatura piÃ¹ corta rispetto al passato visto che il finale scende da 3,46 a 3,15 a tutto vantaggio dellâ€™accelerazione, che vanta un dato di 4,6 secondi sullo 0-100 km/h. |250 km/h di velocitÃ  massima, la nuova GR Supra Manuale sarÃ  proposta anche in una inedita Lightweight Edition che oltre ai 17 kg guadagnati nel passaggio da automatico a manuale, perde 4,8 kg di peso nei cerchi, 5,5 nel sistema multimediale ed 11 kg tra rivestimenti, elettronica e meccanica dei sedili per un totale di -38,3 kg che porta il peso a secco a 1.502 kg DIN.|Pensata per avere una escursione massima di 42 mm (erano partiti da 38) la nuova leva del cambio Ã¨ stata oggetto di un importante studio da parte degli uomini di Gazoo Racing perchÃ© dopo una prima prototipazione con un peso di 68 grammi si Ã¨ arrivati ad un elemento da 200 grammi passando per uno da 137 grammi. Un valore tuttâ€™altro che casuale e che contribuisce nel vincere la resistenza che oppongono gli elementi della trasmissione nei vari passaggi di marcia. Del resto pretendere di avere un cambio leggero come quello di una MX-5 o di una GR86 con un valore di coppia di 500 Nm a 1.600 giri (costanti fino a 4.500) sarebbe stato oggettivamente impossibile. Degno di nota Ã¨ anche lo studio sul sistema di rilascio della frizione che Ã¨ una esclusiva progettuale di Toyota. |McPherson davanti, multilink dietro, la nuova Supra manuale introduce una barra antirollio da 23,5 davanti e 18 mm dietro con nuovi supporti in gomma - caratterizzati da un diverso processo di vulcanizzazione - che consentono di avere maggior rigiditÃ  di insieme e quindi una guida piÃ¹ precisa. Nuove sono anche la taratura degli ammortizzatori e la taratura della servoassistenza elettrica.|Nella Supra GR 2023 si fa notare anche una diversa taratura dei sistemi di controllo di trazione e stabilitÃ : un elemento interessante riguarda la lettura della strada che stiamo percorrendo visto che con percentuali di pendenza superiori al 5% il controllo di trazione si â€œapreâ€ maggiormente, consentendo una guida piÃ¹ sportiva e meno influenzata da interventi elettronici. Sempre che non si decida di disattivare tuttoâ€¦|A livello di guida la nuova GR Supra A90 manuale Ã¨ qualcosa di unico nel proprio genere: ne abbiamo guidate tante di GT manuali, sino a qualche anno fa, ma oggi questo ritorno rappresenta qualcosa di assolutamente controtendenza ed evidentemente frutto di uno studio sulla clientela che ha riportato su strada una vettura molto piacevole da guidare, decisamente piÃ¹ vogliosa di far sentire la propria meccanica a tutti coloro i quali sono in grado di apprezzare un bel cambio manuale piuttosto di un velocissimo ma asettico cambio manuale. Corsa della leva piuttosto contenuta, innesti pesanti ed un â€œfiloâ€gommosi, evidente aiuto elettronico in up-shift e downshift la nuova Supra manuale Ã¨ davvero super gustosa da guidare e girando sulla pista di Monte Blanco viene da chiedersi se questa soluzione starebbe bene anche nella piÃ¹ leggera quattro cilindri (-100 kg) oltre che in questo piccolo capolavoro di tecnica e coraggio che Toyota porta in concessionaria - certo con lo zampino di BMW - per far godere tutti gli appassionati di guida. E questa Ã¨ cosa buona e giusta.|Vi lascio alla mia prova test drive in pista: pochi giri per capire quanto divertente possa essere questo ferro frutto della passione. Poco meno di 70.000 euro il prezzo di listino.|#supramanuale #savethemanuals #masterpilot

title: The Steam Deck's Big Controversy - New vs. Old Fans
description: The Steam Deck switched its fans in some retail units vs. review units, causing some controversy over perceived "noisiness" of the Steam Deck. This tests the Delta vs. Huaying review fans.|Sponsor: Montech Century 850 on Amazon: https://geni.us/s2aV|The Steam Deck launched with a different review unit fan than some retail units are getting, resulting in consumers being unhappy with the noise produced by their Steam Deck. In response, you can control the fan speed (to minimize the noise - though this doesn't fix the noise), replace the fan -- which we show you how to do -- or maybe just return the unit, but that's assuming it's bothering you. In this testing, we have like-for-like comparisons, including Steam Deck Delta fan noise captures vs. review unit (Huaying) fan noise captures.|This is the debut of our frequency spectrum analysis content, but also features something we're very experienced in -- which is noise level testing, except in a much more accurate chamber than ever before. We're still learning frequency spectrum analysis, so our interpretation in some parts will be softer-handed than typically as we want to learn and gain confidence first, but we are already confident in the data collection and quality. This means that you have a lot to work with between our subjective noise comparisons and objective noise comparisons, allowing you to form your own opinion.|RELATED VIDEOS|You can find our in-depth hardware review of the Steam Deck here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NeQH__XVa64|We reviewed the overall user experience & software of the Steam Deck here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UUh2qtjZu4E|Our Steam Deck Teardown is here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dlsJB3narnk|Unboxing the Acoustic Chamber: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n97ot-gXXVw|FRESHLY RESTOCKED GN 'BLUEPRINT' T-SHIRTS! https://store.gamersnexus.net/products/gn-blueprint-shirt-heather-true-royal-t-shirt|Get a GN 'Volt' Anti-Static Modmat, our best-selling item for 4 years now and featuring a high-quality work surface with reference diagrams: https://store.gamersnexus.net/products/modmat-volt-large |Grab the GN Drink Coaster Pack, featuring 3D component designs on high-quality rubber coasters. title: Kasus Penganiayaan Anak DPR, Faisal Marasabessy Jadi Tersangka Hingga Plat RFH Terbukti Palsu!
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Ketua Pemuda Pejuang Bravo 5, Ali Fanser Marasabessydiduga ikut menganiaya Justin Frederick, korban pengeroyokan di Tol Dalam Kota, Sabtu (4/06) lalu.||||Sementara itu, anak Ali, Faisal Marasabessy telah ditetapkan sebagai tersangka.||||Penyelidikan kasus pengeroyokan anak seorang anggota DPR, di Tol Dalam Kota Gatot Subroto Jakarta, masih berjalan.||||Kali ini, polisi membuka dugaan baru Ali Fanser Marasabessy, ayah tersangka Faisal Marasabessy, sekaligus Ketua Pemuda Pejuang Bravo 5, diduga ikut terlibat dalam penganiayaan terhadap korban.||||Saat ini Ali Fanser, masih berstatus sebagai saksi.||||Sejumlah barang bukti disita, termasuk baju dan celana yang dipakai pelaku saat memukul korban.||||Baca Juga Ibu Justin Frederick, Indah Kurnia: Saya Tidak Tega Lihat Video Penganiayaannya! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/296309/ibu-justin-frederick-indah-kurnia-saya-tidak-tega-lihat-video-penganiayaannya||||Sementara itu, Dewan Pimpinan Pusat Organisasi Masyarakat Pejuang Bravo 5, menyebut tidak akan memberikan pendampingan hukum kepada Faisal Marasabessy, yang menjadi tersangka kasus pemukulan putra anggota DPR.||||Perbuatan tersangka di luar tanggung jawab organisasi, dan mendorong kasus ini diproses sesuai dengan hukum yang berlaku.||||Tersangka pengeroyokan anak anggota DPR RI, Justin Frederick diduga pakai plat palsu.||||Pelat nomor RFH yang digunakan pelaku tidak sesuai dengan kendaraan yang digunakan.||||Dari hasil pemeriksaaan Dirlantas Polda Metro Jaya, pelat nomor B 1146 RFH seharusnya untuk mobil sedan.||||Kendaraan milik tersangka, Faisal Marasabessy diduga tak terdaftar atau bodong.||||Dalam video pengeroyokan yang viral di media sosial, mobil milik tersangka Nissan X-Trail warna abu-abu memiliki plat B 1146 RFH atau plat khusus yang biasa digunakan pejabat.||||Faisal Marassabessy dijerat dengan pasal 351 dan atau pasal 170 KUHP tentang penganiayaan dan kekerasan, dengan ancaman hukuman penjara maksimal 9 tahun.||||Sementara ayahnya, Ali Fanser Marassabessy masih berstatus saksi.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296476/kasus-penganiayaan-anak-dpr-faisal-marasabessy-jadi-tersangka-hingga-plat-rfh-terbukti-palsu

title: Gagal Menyalip, 2 Bocah Pengendara Sepeda Motor Tewas Akibat Terlindas Truk Kontainer di Cilincing!
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Dua anak di bawah umur, tewas mengenaskan di Jalan Raya Tugu, Cilincing, Jakarta Utara, Senin (6/06) malam.||||Keduanya terjatuh dan terlindas truk kontainer, saat mengendarai sepeda motor.||||Dari video yang diambil warga, dua pengendara sepeda motor yang berboncengan ini meninggal dunia dengan luka parah di bagian kepala setelah terlindas truk kontainer di Jalan Tugu, Cilincing, Jakarta Utara, Senin (6/06) malam.||||Dari kesaksian warga, kedua korban yang masih di bawah umur, berboncengan menggunakan sepeda motor menuju Simpang Lima Semper.||||Baca Juga Lagi-Lagi Demi Konten, Dua Bocah Nekat Hadang Truk Hingga Akhirnya Tertabrak! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/295432/lagi-lagi-demi-konten-dua-bocah-nekat-hadang-truk-hingga-akhirnya-tertabrak||||Korban berusaha menyalip sebuah truk kontainer.||||Namun nahas, dari arah berlawanan muncul sebuah truk kontainer lainnya.||||Korban yang berusaha menghindar, justru hilang kendali hingga terjatuh.||||Kedua korban bersama sepeda motornya lalu tergilas truk kontainer.||||Kedua jenazah dibawa ke Rumah Sakit Cipto Mangunkusumo.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296463/gagal-menyalip-2-bocah-pengendara-sepeda-motor-tewas-akibat-terlindas-truk-kontainer-di-cilincing

title: Khilafatul Muslimin Gunakan Strategi Non-Kekerasan, Pengamat : Masyarakat Tertipu & Ingin Bergabung
description: BANDAR LAMPUNG, KOMPAS.TV - Polisi melakukan penangkan pimpinan Khilafatul Muslimin yang berpusat di Lampung.||||Abdul Qadir Baraja ditangkap di kediamannya yang juga satu lokasi dengan kantor pusat Khilafatul Muslimin di Teluk Betung, Sukaraja, Bandar Lampung.||||Sebelumnya, polisi juga menetapkan tiga orang tersangka dalam kasus konvoi Khilafatul Muslimin, di Brebes Jawa Tengah.||||Ketiganya ditetapkan tersangka karena diduga menyebarkan berita bohong atau hoaks, atau percobaan makar lewat kampanye khilafah.||||Tersangka yang telah ditetapkan polisi adalah, seorang pimpinan cabang jemaah Khilafatul Muslimin Brebes, dan dua pimpinan ranting di Sikumbang dan Keboledan.||||Mereka kini ditahan di Polres Brebes, dan terancam hukuman penjara selama 15 tahun.||||Terkait kasus ini, Polres Brebes, Jawa Tengah menyita sejumlah atribut dan buku yang digunakan para tersangka saat konvoi.||||Berdasarkan hasil pemeriksaan, kegiatan ini dilakukan para tersangka di brebes dan telah berlangsung sejak 2014.||||Polisi kini masih mendalami terkait paham radikal dan aliran finansial untuk kelompok tersebut.||||Sebelumnya, konvoi puluhan motor dengan membawa atribut dan bendera bertuliskan Khilafatul Muslimin terjadi di Brebes, Jawa Tengah.||||Dalam rekaman video yang tersebar di media sosial, saat konvoi kelompok ini juga membagikan selebaran mengenai khilafah kepada masyarakat.||||Selain di Brebes, aksi konvoi Khilafatul Muslimin ini juga terjadi di Bandung, dan Jakarta Timur.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296428/khilafatul-muslimin-gunakan-strategi-non-kekerasan-pengamat-masyarakat-tertipu-ingin-bergabung
tags: abdul qadir baraja|khilafatul muslimin|khilfatul buat negara|lampung|radikalisme|strategi khilafatul

title: Tak Hanya Umat Muslim, Khilafatul Muslimin Juga Rekrut Penganut Agama Lain untuk Bergabung!
description: BANDAR LAMPUNG, KOMPAS.TV - Polisi melakukan penangkan pimpinan Khilafatul Muslimin yang berpusat di Lampung.||||Abdul Qadir Baraja ditangkap di kediamannya yang juga satu lokasi dengan kantor pusat Khilafatul Muslimin di Teluk Betung, Sukaraja, Bandar Lampung.||||Sebelumnya, polisi juga menetapkan tiga orang tersangka dalam kasus konvoi Khilafatul Muslimin, di Brebes Jawa Tengah.||||Ketiganya ditetapkan tersangka karena diduga menyebarkan berita bohong atau hoaks, atau percobaan makar lewat kampanye khilafah.||||Tersangka yang telah ditetapkan polisi adalah, seorang pimpinan cabang jemaah Khilafatul Muslimin Brebes, dan dua pimpinan ranting di Sikumbang dan Keboledan.||||Mereka kini ditahan di Polres Brebes, dan terancam hukuman penjara selama 15 tahun.||||Terkait kasus ini, Polres Brebes, Jawa Tengah menyita sejumlah atribut dan buku yang digunakan para tersangka saat konvoi.||||Berdasarkan hasil pemeriksaan, kegiatan ini dilakukan para tersangka di Brebes dan telah berlangsung sejak 2014.||||Polisi kini masih mendalami terkait paham radikal dan aliran finansial untuk kelompok tersebut.||||Sebelumnya, konvoi puluhan motor dengan membawa atribut dan bendera bertuliskan Khilafatul Muslimin terjadi di Brebes, Jawa Tengah.||||Dalam rekaman video yang tersebar di media sosial, saat konvoi kelompok ini juga membagikan selebaran mengenai khilafah kepada masyarakat.||||Selain di Brebes, aksi konvoi Khilafatul Muslimin ini juga terjadi di Bandung, dan Jakarta Timur.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296417/tak-hanya-umat-muslim-khilafatul-muslimin-juga-rekrut-penganut-agama-lain-untuk-bergabung
tags: abdul qadir baraja|anti demokrasi|khilafatul muslimin|lampung|non-muslim

title: Prince Harry and Meghan Markle's Daughter Lilibet Has RED HAIR!
description: Meghan Markle and Prince Harry are sharing a new photo of their little girl! On Monday, the couple shared a picture of their daughter, Lilibet, which was taken during her first birthday party at Frogmore Cottage. A source is giving ET details about the celebration, revealing there were several relatives in attendance, including Princess Anne's children, Zara Tindall and Peter Phillips, along with their spouses and children. The source also notes the party on Saturday was an opportunity for the young children who are close in age to spend some time together. The insider says that it was low-key and relaxed with a birthday cake for all the kids to enjoy.

title: Ina Garten's Kitchen Clambake | Barefoot Contessa | Food Network
description: Ina loads her kitchen clambake with kielbasa, clams, mussels and shrimp steamed in a leek and white wine broth for a taste of the sea without the sand!|Subscribe to #discoveryplus to stream more of #BarefootContessa: http://discoverypl.us/2NeKVgd|Get the recipe â–¶ https://foodtv.com/39arJeV|Subscribe to Food Network â–¶ http://foodtv.com/YouTube|Ina throws open the doors of her Hamptons home for delicious food, dazzling entertaining ideas and good fun on Barefoot Contessa.|Welcome to Food Network, where learning to cook is as simple as clicking play! Grab your apron and get ready to get cookin' with some of the best chefs around the world. We'll give you a behind-the-scenes look at our best shows, take you inside our favorite restaurant and be your resource in the kitchen to make sure every meal is a 10/10!|Kitchen Clambake|RECIPE COURTESY OF INA GARTEN|Level: Intermediate|Total: 1 hr|Prep: 30 min|Cook: 30 min|Yield: 6 to 8 servings|Ingredients|1 1/2 pounds kielbasa|3 cups chopped yellow onions (2 large onions)|2 cups chopped leeks, well cleaned (2 leeks, white parts only)|1/4 cup good olive oil|1 1/2 pounds small potatoes (red or white)|1 tablespoon kosher salt|1/2 tablespoon freshly ground black pepper|2 dozen littleneck clams, scrubbed|2 dozen steamer clams, scrubbed|2 pounds mussels, cleaned and debearded|1 1/2 pounds large shrimp, in the shell|3 (1 1/2 pound) lobsters|2 cups good dry white wine|Directions|Directions|Slice the kielbasa diagonally into 1-inch thick slices. Set aside. Saute the onions and leeks in the olive oil in a heavy-bottomed 16 to 20 quart stockpot over medium heat for 15 minutes, until the onions start to brown.|Layer the ingredients on top of the onions in the stockpot in this order: first the potatoes, salt, and pepper; then the kielbasa, little neck clams, steamer clams, mussels, shrimp, and lobsters. Pour in the white wine. Cover the pot tightly and cook over medium-high heat until steam just begins to escape from the lid, about 15 minutes. Lower the heat to medium and cook another 15 minutes. The clambake should be done. Test to be sure the potatoes are tender, the lobsters are cooked, and the clams and mussels are open. Remove the lobsters to a wooden board, cut them up, and crack the claws. With large slotted spoons, remove the seafood, potatoes, and sausages to a large bowl and top with the lobsters. Season the broth in the pot to taste, and ladle over the seafood, being very careful to avoid any sand in the bottom.|Subscribe to our channel to fill up on the latest must-eat recipes, brilliant kitchen hacks and content from your favorite Food Network shows.|â–¶ FOOD NETWORK KITCHEN APP: http://foodtv.com/FNKApp|â–¶ WEBSITE: https://www.foodnetwork.com|â–¶ FULL EPISODES: https://watch.foodnetwork.com|â–¶ FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/FoodNetwork|â–¶ INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/FoodNetwork|â–¶ TWITTER: https://twitter.com/FoodNetwork|#InaGarten #BarefootContessa #FoodNetwork #KitchenClambake|Ina Garten's Kitchen Clambake | Barefoot Contessa | Food Network|https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aVeas0P2pfQ

title: Kerala governor rebukes Qatar; Says apology demand to India 'not  important' over Prophet insult
description: Kerala Governor Arif Mohammed Khan has brushed aside the public apology demand by Qatar over the controversial remarks made by now-suspended and expelled BJP leaders against Prophet Mohammad. The Governor said that people should pay attention to the Prime Minister and the RSS Chief's calls for strengthening India's tradition of inclusiveness. He further added, 'People are entitled to their opinions. How does it matter? The demand for apology is not important. India cannot bother about such small reactions.' Arif Mohammed Khan said what India had to be careful about was protecting its own traditions. Watch this report to know more.|#KeralaGovernorRebukesQatar #ArifMohammedKhan #PublicApologyNotImportant #ProphetMohammedInsulted #BJP #RSS #QatarDemands #NupurSharma #NaveenJindal #prophetmuhammad #NoPublicApology #Delhi

title: Netflix's The Sandman Trailer: Who's Who in the DC Comics Show
description: Not every big-budget DC series is heading to HBO Max in 2022. We've just gotten a closer look at Netflix's ambitious and extremely expensive adaptation of The Sandman. The first Sandman trailer showcases many of the key heroes and villains who will shape the story in Season 1 of the Netflix show.||||But don't worry if you can't tell Dream from Desire from Jenna Coleman's Johanna Constantine. We're here to break down all the familiar faces in this new footage so you're ready for The Sandman when it drops in August 2022.||||The trailer opens with several shots of Tom Sturridge as Morpheus, the main protagonist of the series and the titular Sandman himself. Morpheus is also known as Dream. One of the seven immortal beings known as The Endless, Morpheus rules over a realm called The Dreaming, which is shaped by the dreams of mortals.||||While executive producer Neil Gaiman has hinted the series isn't exactly a 1:1 adaptation of the comics, it definitely looks as though Season 1 will follow the events of the first Sandman graphic novel, Preludes and Nocturnes.||||For more on all these characters, plus The Corinthian, Matthew the Raven, and Gwendoline Christie as Lucifer Morningstar, watch our full The Sandman trailer breakdown.|#IGN #Netflix

title: Abdul Qadir Baraja Ditangkap, Eks NII :Tidak Kaget, Mereka Bahkan Ingin Buat Pemerintahan Sendiri
description: BANDAR LAMPUNG, KOMPAS.TV - Polisi melakukan penangkan pimpinan Khilafatul Muslimin yang berpusat di Lampung.||||Abdul Qadir Baraja ditangkap di kediamannya yang juga satu lokasi dengan kantor pusat Khilafatul Muslimin di Teluk Betung, Sukaraja, Bandar Lampung.||||Sebelumnya, polisi juga menetapkan tiga orang tersangka dalam kasus konvoi Khilafatul Muslimin, di Brebes Jawa Tengah.||||Ketiganya ditetapkan tersangka karena diduga menyebarkan berita bohong atau hoaks, atau percobaan makar lewat kampanye khilafah.||||Tersangka yang telah ditetapkan polisi adalah, seorang pimpinan cabang jemaah Khilafatul Muslimin Brebes, dan dua pimpinan ranting di Sikumbang dan Keboledan.||||Baca Juga Situasi TKP Penangkapan Abdul Qadir Baraja, Pimpinan Khilafatul Muslimin di Bandar Lampung! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/296385/situasi-tkp-penangkapan-abdul-qadir-baraja-pimpinan-khilafatul-muslimin-di-bandar-lampung||||Mereka kini ditahan di Polres Brebes, dan terancam hukuman penjara selama 15 tahun.||||Terkait kasus ini, Polres Brebes, Jawa Tengah menyita sejumlah atribut dan buku yang digunakan para tersangka saat konvoi.||||Berdasarkan hasil pemeriksaan, kegiatan ini dilakukan para tersangka di brebes dan telah berlangsung sejak 2014.||||Polisi kini masih mendalami terkait paham radikal dan aliran finansial untuk kelompok tersebut.||||Sebelumnya, konvoi puluhan motor dengan membawa atribut dan bendera bertuliskan Khilafatul Muslimin terjadi di Brebes, Jawa Tengah.||||Dalam rekaman video yang tersebar di media sosial, saat konvoi kelompok ini juga membagikan selebaran mengenai khilafah kepada masyarakat.||||Selain di Brebes, aksi konvoi Khilafatul Muslimin ini juga terjadi di Bandung, dan Jakarta Timur.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296387/abdul-qadir-baraja-ditangkap-nii-saya-tidak-kaget-mereka-bahkan-ingin-buat-pemerintahan-sendiri
tags: abdul qadir baraja|khilafatul muslimin|konvoi|lampung|nii|radikal

title: Doa Anies Usai Takziah ke Ridwan Kamil: Eril Jadi Pembuka Pintu Jannah Bagi Orang Tua
description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS TV  Gubernur DKI Jakarta Anies Baswedan bertakziah ke Gedung Pakuan Bandung pada Senin (6/6) temui Ridwan Kamil.||||Kedatangan Anies beserta istri untuk mendokan keluarga Ridwan Kamil yang ditinggal putra sulung mereka, Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz.||||"Menyampaikan ungkapan belasungkawa rasa duka cita kami, pribadi, keluarga, dan atas nama warga Jakarta," ujar Anies usai bertemu Ridwan Kamil.||||Baca Juga Penjelasan Soal Hanyutnya Eril, Ridwan Kamil Sebut Putra Sulungnya Lindungi Ibunya di https://www.kompas.tv/article/296325/penjelasan-soal-hanyutnya-eril-ridwan-kamil-sebut-putra-sulungnya-lindungi-ibunya||||"Tentu kita mendengar cerita, ngobrol, mendengar penuturan banyak hal," ucapnya.||||Atas kejadian yang menimpa Ridwan Kamil dan keluarga, Anies mendoakan agar kebaikan Eril semasa hidup dapat menjadi pembuka pintu surga bagi kedua orang tuanya.||||"Kejadian ini membukakan kita semua pada begitu banyak kebaikan yang Eril lakukan yang ceritanya baru bermunculan sekarang. Insya Allah Eril kusnul khatimah," ucap Anies.||||"Insya Allah Eril akan menjadi pembuka pintu jannah bagi orang tuanya," lanjutnya.||||Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril dinyatakan meninggal dunia usai hilang dan hanyut di sungai Aare, Swiss.||||Hingga kini proses pencarian Eril masih dilakukan. Namun usai tujuh hari sejak hilang, keluarga meyakini Eril meninggal dunia karena tenggelam.||||Selain Anies Baswedan, sejumlah tokoh dan pejabat juga datangi Ridwan Kamil untuk sampaikan pesan duka.||||Video Editor: Laurensius Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296355/doa-anies-usai-takziah-ke-ridwan-kamil-eril-jadi-pembuka-pintu-jannah-bagi-orang-tua
tags: anies baswedan ridwan kamil|anies takziah ridwan kamil|eril meninggal|pengajian eril|ridwan kamil eril sungai aare

title: Ukrainian jet burns fiercely & crashes to the ground; Hit by Russian Su-30 or friendly fire mishap?
description: A Ukrainian fighter was shot down late Sunday evening, videos show the jet burning fiercely. Wreckage pics suggest the downed jet was a Sukhoi Su-27, Russian platforms, however, say it was a MiG-29. Exact cause unknown, 2 versions doing the rounds - was it a friendly fire mishap, or a Russian Su-30 took it down? title: How 'green gentrification' is pricing out longtime East Boston residents
description: The city of Boston faces two enormous problems: Sea level rise in its harbor that is getting worse with climate change and a dearth of affordable housing, pricing out many longtime residents. Solutions to one of the problems may compound the challenge of solving the other, a phenomenon researchers have called this "green gentrification." title: America's past gun control laws might surprise you
description: Despite recent mass shootings in Buffalo, Uvalde, and Tulsa, Americans are pessimistic that new gun safety laws will pass Congress because of partisan polarization. But even in the mythical gun-loving wild west, sheriffs wouldnâ€™t allow guns into town. |David Yamane, a gun-owning sociologist, discusses with Reality Checkâ€™s John Avlon the disconnect between gun mythology in America and its gun culture today.|===|A striking number from a new poll on guns|Analysis by Chris Cillizza, CNN Editor-at-large|As Congress considers, again, the possibility of moving a package of gun control reforms, a number from a new CBS News/YouGov poll jumped out at me as evidence of why solving America's gun violence problem is so hard.|It's this: 44% of Republicans said that mass shootings are something we have to accept as part of a free society. (A majority of Republicans -- 56% -- said mass shootings are something we can prevent and stop if we really tried.)|That number is a striking departure from how the country as a whole views the issue. More than 7 in 10 Americans (72%) said that mass shootings could be prevented if we really tried, while just 28% said they were part of living in a free society.|Consider what those Republicans are saying: There is no policy -- or cultural -- solution to the problem of mass shootings. Instead, it is a necessary evil of living in a free society.|This is, of course, utter bunk.|Plenty of other free countries in the world do not have a mass shooting problem like we do in the United States.|Read more at: https://www.cnn.com/2022/06/06/politics/gun-mass-shootings-politicians-poll/index.html

title: Ridwan Kamil Cerita Momen Susuri Sungai Cari Eril di Sungai Aare: Setiap Hari, Selama Tujuh Hari
description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS TV  Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil kisahkan momen-momen ketika ia susuri sungai mencari sang anak, Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril di Sungai Aare, Swiss.||||Hal tersebut ia sampaikan saat hadiri pengajian keluarga atas kepergian Eril.||||Ridwan Kamil kisahkan upayanya mencari Eril saat itu, di mana ia berjalan menyusuri sungai Aare berharap bertemu Eril.||||Baca Juga [Full] Pernyataan Ridwan Kamil Soal Hilangnya Eril di Sungai Aare, Swiss: Ada Dugaan Kram di https://www.kompas.tv/article/296330/full-pernyataan-ridwan-kamil-soal-hilangnya-eril-di-sungai-aare-swiss-ada-dugaan-kram||||"Sesuai syariatnya, kami berikhtiar, saya tiap hari selama tujuh hari jalan kaki 5 Km - 8 Km, susuri sungai itu berharap bisa segera bertemu (Eril)," kisah Ridwan Kamil.||||Namun usai tujuh hari berlalu, Ridwan Kamil juga taati syariat meyakini Eril meninggal dunia dan melaksanakan salat Ghaib untuk Eril.||||Jumat (3/6) keluarga Ridwan Kamil resmi menyampaikan kabar duka bahwa mereka meyakini Eril meninggal karena tenggelam.||||"Doa saya selalu, Ya Allah saya tidak minta dimudahkan urusan hidup saya, tapi saya minta selalu dikuatkan punggung dan bahu saya, karena pasti akan mendapati ujian-ujian yang akan besar lagi," ujar Ridwan Kamil.||||Kini Ridwan Kamil sudah kembali ke Bandung untuk bertugas selaku Gubernur Jawa Barat.||||Ridwan Kamil dan istrinya Atalia pun sudah muncul ke hadapan publik, menerima pesan-pesan dan doa langsung dari warga Jawa Barat.||||Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril hilang usai hanyut di sungai Aare, Swiss, pada Kamis (26/5).||||Meski sudah dinyatakan meninggal dunia, otoritas Swiss dan KBRI Bern masih melakukan pencarian Eril hingga waktu yang tidak ditentukan.||||Video Editor: Laurensius Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296354/ridwan-kamil-cerita-momen-susuri-sungai-cari-eril-di-sungai-aare-setiap-hari-selama-tujuh-hari

title: Situasi TKP Penangkapan Abdul Qadir Baraja, Pimpinan Khilafatul Muslimin di Bandar Lampung!
description: BANDAR LAMPUNG, KOMPAS.TV - Polisi melakukan penangkan pimpinan Khilafatul Muslimin yang berpusat di Lampung.||||Abdul Qadir Baraja ditangkap di kediamannya yang juga satu lokasi dengan kantor pusat Khilafatul Muslimin di Teluk Betung, Sukaraja, Bandar Lampung.||||Sebelumnya, polisi juga menetapkan tiga orang tersangka dalam kasus konvoi Khilafatul Muslimin, di Brebes Jawa Tengah.||||Ketiganya ditetapkan tersangka karena diduga menyebarkan berita bohong atau hoaks, atau percobaan makar lewat kampanye khilafah.||||Tersangka yang telah ditetapkan polisi adalah, seorang pimpinan cabang jemaah Khilafatul Muslimin Brebes, dan dua pimpinan ranting di Sikumbang dan Keboledan.||||Baca Juga Sebarkan Berita Bohong & Bertentangan dengan Pancasila, Polisi Tangkap Pimpinan Khilafatul Muslimin! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/296382/sebarkan-berita-bohong-bertentangan-dengan-pancasila-polisi-tangkap-pimpinan-khilafatul-muslimin||||Mereka kini ditahan di Polres Brebes, dan terancam hukuman penjara selama 15 tahun.||||Terkait kasus ini, Polres Brebes, Jawa Tengah menyita sejumlah atribut dan buku yang digunakan para tersangka saat konvoi.||||Berdasarkan hasil pemeriksaan, kegiatan ini dilakukan para tersangka di brebes dan telah berlangsung sejak 2014.||||Polisi kini masih mendalami terkait paham radikal dan aliran finansial untuk kelompok tersebut.||||Sebelumnya, konvoi puluhan motor dengan membawa atribut dan bendera bertuliskan Khilafatul Muslimin terjadi di Brebes, Jawa Tengah.||||Dalam rekaman video yang tersebar di media sosial, saat konvoi kelompok ini juga membagikan selebaran mengenai khilafah kepada masyarakat.||||Selain di Brebes, aksi konvoi Khilafatul Muslimin ini juga terjadi di Bandung, dan Jakarta Timur.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296385/situasi-tkp-penangkapan-abdul-qadir-baraja-pimpinan-khilafatul-muslimin-di-bandar-lampung

title: Mahfud MD Mengaku Terharu Mendengar Pesan Buya Syafii Maarif Sebelum Meninggal - ROSI
description: KOMPASTV - Mahfud MD mengaku terharu atas pesan yang disampaikan Buya Syafii Maarif kepada Ketua Umum PP Muhammadiyah Haedar Nashir sebelum meninggal. Buya Syafii menyampaikan sudah memesan tanah pemakamannya sendiri pada tanggal 14 Februari lalu. Padahal beliau berhak dimakamkan taman makam pahlawan. |Selengkapnya hanya di dialog Rosianna Silalahi bersama Mahfud MD (Menko Polhukam), Haedar Nashir (Ketua Umum PP Muhammadiyah), Yahya Cholil Staquf (Ketua Umum PBNU), Yenny Wahid (Direktur Wahid Foundation), Jaya Suprana (Budayawan), Abdul Rohim Ghazali (Direktur Eksekutif Maarif Institute), dan Erik Tauvani Somae (Penulis Buku â€œMozaik Keteladanan Buya Syafii Maarifâ€) dalam ROSI Eps. Buya Syafii Dalam Kenangan: Membumikan Pancasila. Tayang Kamis, 2 Juni 2022 pukul 20.30 WIB hanya di Kompas TV, Independen Terpercaya. |Full Dialog: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jjQK8RX6Utw|Jangan lewatkan dialog seru lainnya di program ROSI setiap hari Kamis pukul 20.30 WIB hanya di @kompastv, Independen Terpercaya.|Follow akun ROSI:|Instagram: @rosi_kompastv|Twitter: RosiKompasTV|Tiktok: Rosi_KompasTV|#RosiKompasTV #TalkshowRosi #KompasTV #Rosi #Talkshow #buyasyafii #buyasyafiimaarif #pancasila #membumikanpancasila #buyasyafiimeninggal #muhammadiyah  ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296373/mahfud-md-mengaku-terharu-mendengar-pesan-buya-syafii-maarif-sebelum-meninggal-rosi

title: Mexico Will Not Attend Summit Of The Americas
description: President Biden is hosting the Summit of the Americas in Los Angeles, this week. Today, the President of Mexico announced that he is refusing to attend as the U.S. is not inviting Cuba, Venezuela, and Nicaragua over their lack of Democratic values. title: The Chicks Are Excited To Perform With Their Kids On 'Gaslighter' Tour

title: Momen Prabowo Subianto Gandeng Megawati Bantu Naiki Tangga di Unhan Bogor
description: BOGOR, KOMPAS.TV - Inilah momen di saat Menhan Prabowo Subianto menggandeng Presiden ke-5 RI sekaligus Ketum PDIP Megawati Soekarnoputri saat menaiki tangga.||||Prabowo Subianto membantu Megawati Soekarnoputri untuk menaiki tangga di Universitas Pertahanan, Bogor pada Senin, 6 Juni 2022.||||Menhan Prabowo, Megawati Soekarnoputri serta sejumlah tokoh lainnya menghadiri sidang promosi terbuka program Doktor Universitas Pertahanan RI program studi ilmu pertahanan, Hasto Kristiyanto.||||Baca Juga Megawati Kesal! title: The Sandman - Official Trailer (2022) Tom Sturridge
description: Check out the trailer for The Sandman, the upcoming series based on the DC comic series written by Neil Gaiman. The Sandman is coming to Netflix on August 5, 2022.||||There is another world that waits for all of us when we close our eyes and sleep â€” a place called the Dreaming, where The Sandman, Master of Dreams (Tom Sturridge), gives shape to all of our deepest fears and fantasies. But when Dream is unexpectedly captured and held prisoner for a century, his absence sets off a series of events that will change both the dreaming and waking worlds forever. To restore order, Dream must journey across different worlds and timelines to mend the mistakes he's made during his vast existence, revisiting old friends and foes, and meeting new entities â€” both cosmic and human â€” along the way.||||The Sandman is developed and executive produced by Gaiman, showrunner Allan Heinberg, and David S. Goyer.|#IGN #Netflix

title: Bret Weinstein: I will be vindicated over Covid
description: Freddie Sayers sits down to discuss the pandemic response with biologist Bret Weinstein.|Before the pandemic, evolutionary biologist and former Evergreen professor Bret Weinstein was lauded by both sides of the political divide for his insights into the crisis on American campuses. As a member of the so-called 'intellectual dark web', Weinstein was expanding his audience and being profiled by legacy media like the New York Times.|Then the pandemic began and his heterodox perspective suddenly fell out of favour, even with many of his erstwhile allies.|Advocating for alternative treatments for Covid, questioning the efficacy of the global vaccine programme and challenging narratives of the pandemic came at a cost. Without warning, the Dark Horse podcast was demonetised on YouTube and Weinstein was forced to split from the views of his former friends and supporters. |So, how can we seek truth in such divided times? Freddie Sayers invited Bret into the UnHerd studio in London to try to understand what his views really are.|Read the supporting article: https://unherd.com/thepost/bret-weinstein-i-will-be/|Listen to the podcast version: https://shows.acast.com/lockdowntv-with-freddie-sayers/bret-weinstein-i-will-be-vindicated-over-covid|Follow UnHerd on social media:|Twitter: https://twitter.com/unherd|Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/unherd/|// TIMECODES // |00:00 - 01:31 - Introduction|01:31 - 04:43 - What have we learnt about the state of the world, post-pandemic?|04:43 - 06:26 - What mistakes were made?|06:26 - 12:31 - Is this pandemic response we experienced, going to become the norm?|12:31 - 14:34 - What does Bret see as the disaster in the pandemic response?|14:34 - 17:50 - Was it worthwhile vaccinating younger people?|17:50 - 22:22 -  Were there darker forces at play when it came to the vaccination programme?|22:22 - 24:48 - Bret discusses the â€˜Better Way conferenceâ€™ he attended|24:48 - 28:33 - What is the worst case scenario behind the pandemic response?|28:33 - 31:14 - In a few decades time, will we see a generation with a decreased lifespan?|31:14 - 39:11 - Bretâ€™s opinion on The Pandemic Treaty|39:11 - 43:30 - What is down the road for us? Will there be a new pandemic? |43:30 - 45:36 - Whatâ€™s in store for Bret?|45:36 - 47:29 - Is the worst still yet to come?|47:29 - 48:11 - Conclusion|#UnHerd #COVID #BretWeinstein

title: HYPERCAR MADNESS! Never Seen So Many Epic Cars Together
description: It's time for THE EVENT 2! Joining @The Triple F Collection to support Make A Wish, the line-up is truly phenomenal, with my hypercars closely concentrated in one spot than you will ever see elsewhere!|It's been a while since I last caught up with @The Triple F Collection and my goodness has their garage grown since with the arrival of a LaFerrari, Ford GT, Huayra Roadster BC, Speedtail and so much more. However, not only did the team bring out their full display, but joined also by both @The Hamilton Collection and RLS Collection, plus a fantastic display from @Miller Motorcars too.|Not only that, but Mouse Motors brought along the truly fantastic McLaren F1, by far the star of the show, even with a line-up including multiple Paganis, a Divo amongst other Bugattis, and every hypercar you could want to see. Let's go for a full exploration of all the cars together, both the hypercar paddock and the supercar parking as well, before it's time for everything to shuffle around.|With the sounds of engines rumbling to move out, Evan from Miller Motorcars, very kindly entrusted @TheStradman and I to manoeuvre their F40 and F50 out to the truck. Certainly, not something I'm complaining about!|My mistake, was not realising Mike @Street Speed 717 was there with his SVJ! In the post-Gumball tiredness, I didn't click that it was his SVJ, but hopefully we'll be able to meet up again soon for a fun crossover.|Thanks for watching, Tim|Chapters:|00:00 Intro|01:11 Hypercar Display|08:59 Supercar Parking|11:09 Corvette & Nissan GTR Lineup|12:08 Jaguar Lineup|12:34 Porsche Lineup|13:01 Lamborghini Lineup|13:54 Ford GT Lineup|15:12 Event Roll-out Time|16:48 Short Drive in a Ferrari F50|21:14 More Cars Departing|23:59 Wrap Up|#Hypercar #TripleFCollection #TheEvent2||||Subscribe: http://bit.ly/Shmee150YT||Website: http://www.shmee150.com||Shop: http://shop.shmee150.com||Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/shmee150||Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/shmee150

title: How one statement created issues for PM Modi on global front? | India Chahta Hai
description: Sharma is party national spokesperson and Jindal is spokesperson and head of media department of BJP Delhi unit.||||Before suspending both the leaders in a press statement, BJP national general secretary, Arun Singh said, "During thousands of years of the history of India, every religion has blossomed and flourished. The Bharatiya Janata Party respects all religions. The BJP strongly denounces insults of any religious personality of any religion. The Bharatiya Janata Party is also strongly against any ideology which insults or demeans any sect or religion. The BJP does not promote such people or philosophy."||||Singh noted that India's Constitution gives the right to every citizen to practice any religion of his/her choice and to honour and respect every religion. "As India celebrates 75th year of its Independence, we are committed to making India a great country where all are equal and everyone lives with dignity, where all are committed to India's unity and integrity, where all enjoy the fruits of growth and development," Singh said.

title: US and South Korea launch 8 missiles in response to North Koreaâ€™s latest missile firings
description: Subscribe to our YouTube channel for free here: |https://sc.mp/subscribe-youtube|The United States and South Korea fired 8 surface-to-surface missiles early on June 6, 2022, a day after South Korea and the US ended joint military drills. The launches off South Koreaâ€™s east coast were in response to North Korea launching a barrage of short-range ballistic missiles on June 5. The South Korean military called the action a demonstration of â€œthe capability and readiness to carry out precision strikesâ€ against the source of North Koreaâ€™s missile launches. North Korea also fired three missiles on May 25, the day after US President Joe Biden ended a trip to Asia in which he had agreed to new measures to deter North Koreaâ€™s intensifying weapons tests. title: Minions: The Rise of Gru | Official Trailer (Universal Pictures) HD
description: In cinemas 1 July|Follow us on Facebook at https://www.facebook.com/MinionsMovieUK |Find us on Instagram at https://www.instagram.com/universalpicturesuk/ |Follow us on Twitter at https://twitter.com/universaluk |Find us on TikTok at https://www.tiktok.com/@universalpicturesuk |http://www.minionsmovie.co.uk|Genre: Action-Comedy |Cast: Steve Carell, Taraji P. Henson, Michelle Yeoh, RZA, Jean-Claude Van Damme, Lucy Lawless, Dolph Lundgren, Danny Trejo, Russell Brand, with Julie Andrews and Alan Arkin|Director: Kyle Balda|Co-Directors: Brad Ableson, Jonathan del Val|Producers: Chris Meledandri, Janet Healy, Chris Renaud|This summer, from the biggest global animated franchise in history, comes the origin story of how the worldâ€™s greatest supervillain first met his iconic Minions, forged cinemaâ€™s most despicable crew and faced off against the most unstoppable criminal force ever assembled in Minions: The Rise of Gru. | |Long before he becomes the master of evil, Gru (OscarÂ® nominee Steve Carell) is just a 12-year-old boy in 1970s suburbia, plotting to take over the world from his basement. Itâ€™s not going particularly well. When Gru crosses paths with the Minions, including Kevin, Stuart, Bob, and Ottoâ€”a new Minion sporting braces and a desperate need to pleaseâ€”this unexpected family joins forces. Together, they build their first lair, design their first weapons, and strive to execute their first missions. | |When the infamous supervillain supergroup, the Vicious 6, oust their leaderâ€”legendary martial arts fighter Wild Knuckles (OscarÂ® winner Alan Arkin)â€” Gru, their most devoted fanboy, interviews to become their newest member. The Vicious 6 is not impressed by the diminutive, wannabe villain, but then Gru outsmarts (and enrages) them, and he suddenly finds himself the mortal enemy of the apex of evil. With Gru on the run, the Minions attempt to master the art of kung fu to help save him, and Gru discovers that even bad guys need a little help from their friends. | |Featuring more spectacular action than any film in Illumination history and packed with the franchiseâ€™s signature subversive humor, Minions: The Rise of Gru stars a thrilling new cast, including, the Vicious 6: Taraji P. Henson as cool and confident leader Belle Bottom, whose chain belt doubles as a lethal disco-ball mace; Jean-Claude Van Damme as the nihilistic Jean Clawed, whoâ€™s armed (literally) with a giant robotic claw; Lucy Lawless as Nunchuck, whose traditional nunâ€™s habit hides her deadly nun-chucks; Dolph Lundgren as Swedish roller-skate champion Svengeance, who dispenses his enemies with spin kicks from his spiked skates; and Danny Trejo as Stronghold, whose giant iron hands are both a menace to others and a burden to him.  |The film also stars Russell Brand as Young Dr. Nefario, an aspiring mad scientist, Michelle Yeoh as Master Chow, an acupuncturist with mad kung fu skills, and OscarÂ® winner Julie Andrews as Gruâ€™s maddeningly self-absorbed mom.| |Steered by the franchiseâ€™s original creators, Minions: The Rise of Gru is produced by visionary Illumination founder and CEO Chris Meledandri and his longtime collaborators Janet Healy and Chris Renaud. The film is directed by returning franchise filmmaker Kyle Balda (Despicable Me 3, Minions), co-directed by Brad Ableson (The Simpsons) and Jonathan del Val (The Secret Life of Pets films), and features the iconic voice of Pierre Coffin as the Minions and a killer â€™70s soundtrack courtesy of legendary Grammy-winning music producer Jack Antonoff.

title: Russia Fires X-22 Missiles Towards Kyiv l What Putinâ€™s Move Says About His War Goals & Fears
description: Ukraine has said that Russian forces fired five X-22 cruise missiles from the Caspian Sea toward Kyiv on June 5. The X-22 missile, also known as Kh-22, is a long-range anti-ship missile developed during the Soviet era. It was intended for use against US Navy aircraft carriers and carrier battle groups, with either a conventional or nuclear warhead. Russiaâ€™s defence ministry said that it targeted tanks and other military supplies donated by the West in Kyiv on June 5. Russiaâ€™s defence ministry said the strikes, first since April 28, on Kyiv outskirts destroyed T-72 tanks supplied by Eastern European countries. However, Ukraineâ€™s railway authority said no military equipment had been stored there. The strikes come after Putin lashed out at Western deliveries of weapons to Ukraine, saying they aim to prolong the war. Putin had warned that Western military deliveries to Ukraine will be destroyed by Russian forces.|#Russia #Ukraine #Zelensky #Putin #X22Missiles #KH22Missiles |CRUX is your daily video news guide to the big events that are shaping our world. description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Inilah pelaku pemukulan anak Anggota DPR RI bernama Justin F di Tol Gatot Subroto, Jakarta Selatan.||||Pelaku bernama Faisal Marasebessy yang telah ditetapkan sebagai tersangka dalam kasus dugaan penganiayaan dan pemukulan Justin F.||||Pelaku pun ditampilkan saat Polda Metro Jaya menggelar konferensi pers pada kasus pemukulan yang dilangsungkan pada Senin, 6 Juni 2022.||||Baca Juga Sekjen PDI Perjuangan soal Penganiayaan Anak Anggota DPR di Tol: Hukum Tak Perbolehkan Kekerasan! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/296178/sekjen-pdi-perjuangan-soal-penganiayaan-anak-anggota-dpr-di-tol-hukum-tak-perbolehkan-kekerasan||||Dalam momen tersebut, tidak ada komentar yang keluar dari mulut pelaku.||||Polisi pun menjelaskan kronologi dari peristiwa ini.||||Kabid Humas Polda Metro Jaya Kombes E Zulpan juga menjelaskan motif dari peristiwa penganiayaan terhadap Justin di Tol Gatot Subroto.||||"Motif yang melatar belakangi kejadian adalah pelaku emosi karena serempetan dengan mobil korban," kata Zulpan di Polda Metro Jaya, Senin (6/6/2022).||||Video Editor: Vila Randita||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296252/begini-tampang-pelaku-pemukulan-justin-anak-anggota-dpr-di-tol-gatot-subroto

description: Full written recipe for Tawa Paneer|Prep time : 20 - 25 mins|Cooking time : 35 - 40 mins|Serves : 3 - 4 people|Base gravy|Ingredients:|OIL | à¤¤à¥‡à¤² 2-3 TBSP|WHOLE SPICES|CUMIN SEEDS | à¤œà¥€à¤°à¤¾ 1 TSP|GREEN CARDAMOM | à¤¹à¤°à¥€ à¤‡à¤²à¤¾à¤¯à¤šà¥€ 2 NOS.|CLOVES | à¤²à¥Œà¤‚à¤— 2-3 NOS.|BLACK PEPPER | à¤•à¤¾à¤²à¥€ à¤®à¤¿à¤°à¥à¤š 2-4 NOS.|CINNAMON | à¤¦à¤¾à¤²à¤šà¥€à¤¨à¥€ 1/2 INCH|BAY LEAF | à¤¤à¥‡à¤œ à¤ªà¤¤à¥à¤¤à¤¾ 1 NOS.|ONIONS | à¤ªà¥à¤¯à¤¾à¤œà¤¼ 3-4 MEDIUM SIZED (SLICED)|GINGER | à¤…à¤¦à¤°à¤• 1 INCH|GARLIC | à¤²à¥‡à¤¹à¤¸à¥à¤¨ 7-8 CLOVES|CORIANDER STEM | à¤¹à¤°à¥‡ à¤§à¤¨à¤¿à¤ à¤•à¤¿ à¤¡à¤¨à¤Ÿà¤² 5-6 NOS.|POWDERED SPICES|TURMERIC POWDER | à¤¹à¤²à¥à¤¦à¥€ à¤ªà¤¾à¤‰à¤¡à¤° 1/4 TSP|SPICY RED CHILLI POWDER | à¤¤à¥€à¤–à¥€ à¤²à¤¾à¤² à¤®à¤¿à¤°à¥à¤š à¤ªà¤¾à¤‰à¤¡à¤° 1 TSP|KASHMIRI RED CHILLI POWDER | à¤•à¤¶à¥à¤®à¥€à¤°à¥€ à¤²à¤¾à¤² à¤®à¤¿à¤°à¥à¤š à¤ªà¤¾à¤‰à¤¡à¤° 1 TSP|CORIANDER POWDER | à¤§à¤¨à¤¿à¤¯à¤¾ à¤ªà¤¾à¤‰à¤¡à¤° 1 TBSP|CUMIN POWDER | à¤œà¥€à¤°à¤¾ à¤ªà¤¾à¤‰à¤¡à¤° 1 TSP|BLACK SALT | à¤•à¤¾à¤²à¤¾ à¤¨à¤®à¤• 1/2 TSP|HOT WATER | à¤—à¤°à¤® à¤ªà¤¾à¤¨à¥€ AS REQUIRED|CAPSICUM | à¤¶à¤¿à¤®à¤²à¤¾ à¤®à¤¿à¤°à¥à¤š 1 NOS. (OPTIONAL)|HOT WATER | garam à¤ªà¤¾à¤¨à¥€ 100-150 ML|WATER | à¤ªà¤¾à¤¨à¥€ AS REQUIRED|Method:|To make the base gravy set a pan on high flame & add the oil into it, once the oil is hot add in all the whole spices & the sliced onions, stir well.|Further add ginger, garlic & coriander stems, stir & cook until the onions turn golden brown, keep stirring at regular intervals.|Once the onions turn golden brown, turn the flame down to low & add all the powdered spices & add hot water immediately to prevent the spices from burning, stir well & cook for 3-4 minutes.|Further add capsicum, tomatoes, green chillies, salt & cashew nuts along with hot water, cover with a lid & cook over medium low flame for 4-5 minutes. |Once the tomatoes get cooked, switch off the flame & cool down the gravy completely, after the gravy cools down you can remove some of the whole spices if you want, then transfer the gravy into a mixer grinder jar & add water as required, blend the gravy finely.|Your base gravy for tawa paneer is ready.|Final gravy|Ingredients:|GHEE | à¤˜à¥€ 2 TBSP + 1 TSP|CUMIN SEEDS | à¤œà¥€à¤°à¤¾ 1 TSP|ONIONS | à¤ªà¥à¤¯à¤¾à¤œà¤¼ 2 MEDIUM SIZED (CHOPPED)|GARLIC | à¤²à¥‡à¤¹à¤¸à¥à¤¨ 2 TBSP (CHOPPED)|GINGER | à¤…à¤¦à¤°à¤• 1 INCH (JULIENNE)|GREEN CHILLIES | à¤¹à¤°à¥€ à¤®à¤¿à¤°à¥à¤š 2-3 NOS. title: Mario Strikers: Battle League | Everything To Know
description: Mario Strikers: Battle League is coming to Nintendo Switch letting you watch some of your favorite Mario characters duke it out on the soccer pitch. Here's everything you need to know about Mario's latest adventure|Mario Strikers: Battle League isnâ€™t exactly the newest FIFA game. Instead, it takes the iconic plumber, and many of his most popular friends and rivals and has them duke it out on the soccer pitch. This video breaks down everything you need to know ahead of the upcoming release of Mario Strikers: Battle League on June 10th.|The game adds a fun arcadey twist to the game of soccer by eliminating all fouls. This means characters will violently and hilariously tackle each other, all in the name of sportsmanship. Donâ€™t worry if you get beat up since getting tackled is one way you will receive items similar to those you might find in a Mario Party or Mario Kart game, letting you even the odds a bit.|Lastly, you can take an awesome final smash style shot where the game will add really cool animations as your character levels an unblockable shot if you time the shot perfectly. Donâ€™t worry if you miss the window, though, as youâ€™ll still have a good chance at making a goal, although if youâ€™re unlucky, the ball might land in the goalieâ€™s hands. Mario Strikers: Battle League comes out exclusively on Nintendo Switch. See you on the pitch!|#MarioStrikers #battleleague

title: 'I Was Stalked By My Driving Instructor' | This Morning
description: Maisie Relph, was so excited to learn how to drive, but little did she know that her driving instructor, Graham Mansie, would become her obsessed nightmare stalker. Even when Maisie moved 200 miles away to go to university, Mansie created fake social media accounts to befriend her and even camped outside her halls of residence. Mansie was last month given a suspended sentence for stalking Maisie, a lifelong ban from contacting her and ordered to go through rehabilitation. title: Mike Maignan is the best goalkeeper of the 2021/22 season | Serie A 2021/22
description: Milan goalkeeper Mike Maignan who wins the award for MVP - Best goalkeeper of Serie A 2021/22. The rankings have been drawn up taking into account the advanced analysis of Stats Perform, formed from the tracking data recorded with the Hawk-Eye system.|These are the characteristics that led to the success of the Rossoneri goalkeeper:|- He holds the record for clean sheets in this Serie A (16) and, since the beginning of 2022, no goalkeeper in the Top 5 European leagues has collected more clean sheets than Maignan (11);|- Among the goalkeepers with more than 10 appearances, he is the one with the highest save rate (78.8%);|- Has the highest win rate (21 out of 31 appearances) in the league (67.7%);|- From 2004/05 to today (since Serie A returned to 20 teams), only Christian Abbiati (18 in 2010/11) has collected more clean sheets than Maignan (16) among Milan goalkeepers in a Serie A league season;|- Also present in the playing phase, Maignan travels an average of 6 km per game.|This is the official channel for the Serie A, providing all the latest highlights, interviews, news and features to keep you up to date with all things Italian football.|Subscribe to the channel here! https://bit.ly/SERIEA_YT| |Find out more about the Serie A at: http://www.legaseriea.it/en/ |Questo Ã¨ il canale ufficiale della Serie A, dove potrai avere accesso ai momenti salienti, alle interviste, alle notizie e alle funzionalitÃ  del momento per rimanere aggiornato sulle ultime novitÃ  del campionato.|Iscriviti qui al canale! https://bit.ly/SERIEA_YT|Per maggiori informazioni sulla Serie A: http://www.legaseriea.it/it

title: Ridwan Kamil Gendong dan Ajak Main Arka Anak Bungsunya Saat Kembali Kerja
description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS.TV  Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil menyempatkan untuk mengajak main Arkana Aidan Misbach yang merupakan anak angkat Ridwan Kamil.||||Ridwan Kamil mengajak Arka bermain di halaman Gedung Sate usai memimpin rapat bersama para Eselon Dua pada Senin, 6 Juni 2022.||||Arka digendong di atas pundak Ridwan Kamil. Sambil bercengkrama, Ridwan Kamil juga mengajak Arka melihat sangkar burung yang ada di halaman Gedung Sate.||||Baca Juga Pihak Keluarga Sampaikan, Ridwan Kamil Mulai Kembali Aktivitas Kedinasannya di https://www.kompas.tv/article/296149/pihak-keluarga-sampaikan-ridwan-kamil-mulai-kembali-aktivitas-kedinasannya||||Sebelumnya, saat tiba di Gedung Sate pagi hari, Ridwan Kamil terlihat menggendong Arka masuk ke ruangan, Ridwan Kamil mengaku dirinya sehat dan terus semangat.||||"Sehat, Alhamdulillah, tetap semangat," ujar Ridwan Kamil.||||Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil kembali bekerja di Gedung Sate setelah cuti mencari anak sulungnya Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril yang hilang di Sungai Aare, Swiss.||||Seperti diketahui anak Ridwan Kamil, Eril hilang di Sungai Aare Swiss pada 26 Mei 2022 lalu.||||Video Editor: Vila Randita||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296159/ridwan-kamil-gendong-dan-ajak-main-arka-anak-bungsunya-saat-kembali-kerja

title: Usai Pimpin Rapat, Ridwan Kamil Bermain Bersama Putranya Arkan
description: KOMPAS.TV - Usai pimpin rapat bersama para eselon dua di Gedung Sate, Bandung, Jawa Barat. Ridwan Kamil menyempatkan diri mengajak bermain putranya Arkan.||||Jurnalis Kompastv Azzi Fardiansyah dan juru kamera Sunandar berkesempatan untuk meliput langsung kegiatan ini.||||Halaman Gedung Sate menjadi lokasi pelepas penat bagi Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil.||||Baca Juga Pihak Keluarga Sampaikan, Ridwan Kamil Mulai Kembali Aktivitas Kedinasannya di https://www.kompas.tv/article/296149/pihak-keluarga-sampaikan-ridwan-kamil-mulai-kembali-aktivitas-kedinasannya||||Usai memimpin rapat bersama para eselon dua di Gedung Sate, Bandung, Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil menyempatkan diri mengajak putranya Arkan untuk bermain.||||Meski masih terlihat begitu sedih namun Ridwan Kamil tetap berkeliling halaman mengikuti keinginan sang anak.||||Lebih dari sepekan tak berjumpa sang ayah, Arkan terlihat begitu senang bisa bermain dengan sang ayah.||||Puas bermain di halaman, Arkan dan Ridwan Kamil berkeliling sejenak di Gedung Sate.||||Arkan mungkin tak paham akan apa yang menimpa sang kakak, namun ketegaran kedua orangtuanya mampu membuat Arkan tetap bahagia meski di tengah duka.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296215/usai-pimpin-rapat-ridwan-kamil-bermain-bersama-putranya-arkan
