title: U.S. & South Korea's tit-for-tat: 8 ballistic missiles fired in Japan sea to counter North Korea
description: In a sharp response to missile tests by North Korea, the United States and South Korea fired eight ballistic missiles. This comes a day after North Korea launched eight short-range ballistic missiles following a South Korea-U.S. joint military exercise involving a U.S. aircraft carrier. A ground-to-ground Army Tactical Missile System (ATACMS) missile was launched at targets in the East Sea, also known as the Sea of Japan, in the early morning. Yonhap news agency reported that the militaries of South Korea and the United States fired eight surface-to-surface missiles over 10 minutes starting at 4:45 am. U.S. Indo-Pacific Command said the exercise included one U.S. Army missile and seven from South Korea. Watch this video for more details.|#us #northkorea #unitedstates #southkorea #seoul #ballistic_missile #missile #missilelaunch #japan #indopacific #joebiden #kimjongun

title: Depot blast in Bangladesh kills nearly 50 people  - BBC News
description: A deadly explosion at a storage depot near the city of Chittagong,  Bangladesh, was said to be heard several kilometres away and shattered windows of nearby buildings. |Hundreds of people had arrived at the site in Sitakunda to tackle the fire when a number of shipping containers exploded.|At least 49 people were killed, while Chittagong's chief doctor has said more than 300 people were injured in total.|Bangladesh's government has promised a fair investigation into the cause of the fire.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#Bangladesh #BBCNews

title: Pro-Khalistan slogans at Golden temple; Bhindranwale posters displayed on Op Blue Star anniversary
description: Pro-Khalistan slogans were raised by supporters of radical Sikh outfits at the Golden Temple in Amritsar on the 38th anniversary of Operation Bluestar. Many youths held banners and placards with â€˜Khalistan Zindabadâ€™ written on them. They wore t-shirts with the picture of slain separatist leader Jarnail Singh Bhindranwale. The protests took place despite prohibitory order being imposed about the Sikh Shrine. Meanwhile, Akal Takht chief Giani Harpreet Singh has stirred up a controversy by calling for weapons training for all Sikhs. The Jathedar of the Takht said Sikhs should start weapons training academies where people could learn to use state-of-the-art weapons. title: 2 in 1 Kheer - Sabudana Vermicelli Kheer Recipe in 10 Mins | Sabudana & Semiya Payasam - Sago Kheer
description: full recipe: https://hebbarskitchen.com/sabudana-vermicelli-kheer-recipe/|sabudana vermicelli kheer recipe | Sabudana And Semiya Payasam - Sago Payasam with detailed photo and video recipe. Perhaps one of the simple, easy and creamy milk pudding dessert recipes made with vermicelli and sago pearls. Basically, a combination of 2 kheer recipes to make perfect and super creamy dessert recipes for all occasions. It is even loaded with a generous amount of nuts which makes it super likeable by all age groups and more importantly for any occasion.|sabudana vermicelli kheer recipe | Sabudana And Semiya Payasam - Sago Payasam with step by step photo and video recipe. Milk-based desserts or kheer recipes are super typical in Indian cuisine. Generally, it is prepared by mixing rice and creamy thick milk which is later cooked and boiled to get a creamy milk dessert. But there are so many variations to this simple dessert recipe. One such simple variation is sabudana vermicelli kheer recipe where both sago pearls and semiya is cooked together as an alternative to rice.|#hebbarskitchen

title: Kurangi Emisi Karbon Ala Formula E - Insight with Desi Anwar
description: Indonesia untuk pertama kalinya menjadi tuan rumah balapan mobil listrik atau Formula E yang diselenggarakan pada 4 Juni 2022. Balapan mobil listrik ini diklaim hanya menghasilkan satu persen emisi karbon. Melalui ajang ini, diharapkan bisa mendukung upaya pemerintah dalam mencapai Net Zero Emissions pada 2060 mendatang. Insight with Desi Anwar bersama Ahmad Sahroni (Chairman Organizing Committee 2022 Jakarta E-Prix) akan membahas bagaimana kontribusi ajang Formula E terhadap keberlanjutan lingkungan.

title: Malai ki Sabzi | à¤®à¤²à¤¾à¤ˆ à¤•à¥€ à¤¸à¤¬à¥à¥›à¥€ | Quick and Easy Recipe | Sanjeev Kapoor Khazana
description: The name might sound confusing, but this dish is here to make you wanting for more!|Fresh malai / cream, sauteed with spices to make a delicious, lip smacking sabzi that goes perfectly with paranthas or nans or even rice!|MALAI KI SABZI|Ingredients|350 grams fresh malai|2 tbsps oil|1 tsp cumin seeds|1 tbsp chopped garlic|Â½ tbsp chopped ginger|2 green chillies, chopped|1 large onion, finely chopped|1 large tomato, finely chopped|Salt to taste|1 tsp sugar|1 tsp red chilli powder|1 tbsp coriander powder|1 tsp cumin powder|Â½ tsp turmeric powder|Â½ tsp garam masala powder|Â¼ tsp roasted dried fenugreek leaves (kasuri methi) powder|2-3 tbsps chopped fresh coriander leaves|Fresh coriander sprig for garnish|Paranthe to serve|Method|1. Heat oil in a non-stick pan. Add cumin seeds and let them change colour.|2. Add garlic, ginger, and green chillies and sautÃ© for 1 minute. Add onion, mix and cook till it turns golden brown.|3. Add tomato, salt and sugar and mix well. Cook till it turns soft and pulpy.|4. Add red chilli powder, coriander powder, cumin powder and turmeric powder and mix well. Cook for 1 minute.|5. Add fresh malai and mix well. Cook for 1-2 minutes. |6. Add garam masala powder, roasted dried fenugreek leaves powder, and coriander leaves and mix well. |7. title: Anggota Bravo Lima Jadi Tersangka Penganiaya Anak Anggota DPR
description: KOMPAS.TV - Polisi menetapkan satu orang tersangka dalam kasus penganiayaan yang menimpa anak seorang anggota DPR.||||Polisi juga menyebut, pelat nomor RFH yang digunakan pelaku tidak sesuai dengan kendaraan yang digunakan pelaku.||||Baca Juga Kronologi Penganiayaan Putra Politikus PDIP Indah Kurnia versi Bravo Lima di https://www.kompas.tv/article/295984/kronologi-penganiayaan-putra-politikus-pdip-indah-kurnia-versi-bravo-lima||||Dari pemeriksaan yang dilakukan Dirlantas Polda Metro Jaya pelat nomor B 1146 RFH bukanlah pelat nomor untuk Nissan Xtrail yang digunakan pelaku.||||Melainkan merupakan pelat untuk kendaraan lain, satu orang ditetapkan sebagai tersangka yaitu Faisal Marasabessy yang juga merupakan anggota Ormas Bravo Lima||||Sabtu siang, keributan terjadi di ruas tol dalam kota arah Cawang. Seorang pengendara bernama Justin Frederick terlibat cek cok dengan pengendara lain yang menggunakan mobil Nissan Xtrail berplat RFH.||||Dari video yang beredar di media sosial, dua orang yang berasal dari mobil berplat RFH menganiaya korban justin hingga babak belur.||||Kasus semakin ramai setelah diketahui korban merupakan anak dari anggota DPR Komisi XI Indah Kurnia.||||Sementara pelaku merupakan ayah dan anak anggota Ormas Pemuda Bravo Lima.||||Pelaku pertama adalah Ali Marasabessy yang merupakan Ketua Ormas Pemuda Bravo Lima.||||Dan pelaku lain adalah Faisal Marasabessy yang merupakan anak Ali Marasabessy, yang juga anggota Ormas Pemuda Bravo Lima, satu orang sudah ditetapkan sebagai tersangka.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296209/anggota-bravo-lima-jadi-tersangka-penganiaya-anak-anggota-dpr

title: SBY dan AHY Bertemu Surya Paloh, Koalisi Pilpres 2024 atau Silaturahmi Semata?
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Di Nasdem Tower, Gondangdia, Menteng, Jakarta Pusat, Minggu (5/6) malam; tuan rumah, Ketua Umum Partai Nasdem, Surya Paloh, kedatangan kawan lama, yakni Ketua Majelis Tinggi Partai Demokrat Susilo Bambang Yudhoyono (SBY).||||SBY, ditemani Ketua Umum Partai Demokrat, Agus Harimurti Yudhoyono (AHY) dan Sekretaris Majelis Tinggi Partai Demokrat, Andi Mallarangeng.||||Pertemuan hanya sebagai silaturahmi dua kawan lama.||||Namun, menurut sumber Kompas TV, isi pertemuan terkait kemungkinan koalisi bersama di Pilpres 2024.||||Siapa pun yang ditentukan sebagai pasangan calon presiden dan wakil presiden, adalah hasil kesepakatan bersama.||||Partai Nasdem dan Surya Paloh, dalam beberapa bulan terakhir, menjadi primadona kunjungan pimpinan partai-partai besar.||||Yang awal adalah Ketua Umum Partai Golkar, Airlangga Hartarto.||||Kemudian yang baru-baru ini datang adalah Ketua Umum Partai Gerindra, Prabowo Subianto.||||Dari partai-partai besar di Pemilu 2019, hanya PDI Perjuangan yang belum bersua.||||Ada Ketua Umum PDI Perjuangan, Megawati Sukarnoputri yang belum bisa ditemui Ketua Umum Partai Nasdem.||||Lantas, apakah pertemuan tersebut akan terjadi?||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296212/sby-dan-ahy-bertemu-surya-paloh-koalisi-pilpres-2024-atau-silaturahmi-semata

title: Prophet remark row: India raps Islamic Nations bodyâ€™s â€˜unwarranted & divisiveâ€™ statement
description: India took strong objection to a statement released by Organisation of Islamic Cooperation (OIC) amid the ongoing controversy over suspended BJP spokesperson, Nupur Sharma's remarks on the Prophet. The spokesperson for the External Affairs Ministry in his statement called OIC's comment unwarranted and divisive, "We have seen the statement on India from the General Secretariat of the Organisation of Islamic Cooperation (OIC). The government of India categorically rejects OIC Secretariat's unwarranted and narrow-minded comments. It is regrettable that the OIC Secretariat has yet again chosen to make motivated, misleading and mischievous comments. This only exposes its divisive agenda being pursued at the behest of vested interests. We would urge the OIC Secretariat to stop pursuing its communal approach and show due respect to all faiths and religions,â€ said Arindam Bagchi. title: Britain defies Putinâ€™s warning; UK to gift M270 MLRS to Ukraine in defence against Russia
description: Just a day after Russian President Vladimir Putin once again warned the West against sending weapons to Ukraine amid Russia's invasion, the UK has decided to arm Ukraine with M270 multiple launch rocket systems. Britain will soon send the rocket launchers to Ukraine which can reach targets up to 80 kilometres. UK said that its move will help Ukraine defence itself better against Russia's invasion. Earlier, U.S. President Joe Biden had refused to send M270 MLRS to Ukraine, claiming that the weapons could reach into Russian territory and that it would not arm Ukraine with any such weapons. Watch this video for more details.|#uk #ukraine #mlrs #russia #russiaukrainewar #vladimirputin #putin #zelensky #borisjohnson #zelenskyy #zelenskiy #britain #rockets #rocketlauncher

title: Saudi, Bahrain, Pak join Islamic nations in condemning ex-BJP spokesperson's Prophet remark
description: Saudi Arabia is the latest among Islamic countries who have slammed Nupur Sharmaâ€™s remarks on Prophet Muhammad. Saudi Arabia's foreign ministry in a statement  reiterated the country's position calling for respect of beliefs and religions and also welcomed BJP's move to suspend its spokesperson. After Pakistan Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif took to Twitter to condemn the remarks by suspended BJP leader, where he called on the world to take note of them, Pakistan Foreign Ministry issued a statement. "BJPâ€™s attempted clarification and belated and perfunctory disciplinary action against these individuals cannot assuage the pain and anguish they have caused to the Muslim world. Muslims residing in India are equally outraged by the completely repugnant comments by the two BJP officials. The ensuing communal violence in Kanpur and in other parts of India bears testimony to this fact," it read. title: BREAKING NEWS:  Perkembangan Terkini Pencarian Emmiril Kahn Mumtadz
description: KOMPAS.TV  Setelah perpanjangan cutinnya berakhir 4 Juni lalu hari ini Ridwan Kamil kembali bertugas sebagai Gubernur Jawa Barat.||||Salah satu agenda Ridwan Kamil hari ini adalah menggelar rapat pimpinan di Gedung Sate.||||Dengan membawa adik angkat Eril yang paling kecil Arkana Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil tiba di Gedung Sate sekitar pukul setengah 11:00 siang.||||Baca Juga Pilu Ridwan Kamil untuk Eril: Seandainya Kami Bisa Bertukar Tempat... di https://www.kompas.tv/article/295990/pilu-ridwan-kamil-untuk-eril-seandainya-kami-bisa-bertukar-tempat||||Sejumlah agenda kerja telah menanti Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil setelah sempat memperpanjang cuti untuk mencari putra sulungnya Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz yang diduga meninggal karena tenggelam di Sungai Aare, Swiss.||||Selain melakukan agenda kedinasan rencananya sore nanti Ridwan Kamil dan keluarga juga akan menggelar pengajian di rumah dinasnya di Gedung Pakuan, Bandung, Jawa Barat.||||Agenda hari ini pihak KBRI dan perwakilan keluarga Ridwan Kamil akan melaporkan proses pencarian yang dilakukan hingga saat ini.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296126/breaking-news-perkembangan-terkini-pencarian-emmiril-khan-mumtadz

title: "Modi Ji, What You Permit...": Telangana's KTR's Swipe Amid Arab Backlash
description: Telangana Minister K T Rama Rao has targeted the centre over the backlash from the Gulf following remarks by BJP spokespersons on Prophet Muhammad. Mr Rao, popularly known as KTR, has questioned why India as a country should apologise for the "hate speeches of BJP bigots".|Addressing the Prime Minister, he said his party should apologise to Indians at home for "spewing and spreading hatred day in day out". title: Saat Presiden Jokowi ajak PM Australia Bersepeda Pagi, Kebun Raya Bogor, 6 Juni 2022
description: *Diplomasi Sepeda Bambu ala Presiden Jokowi*|Ada yang menarik dalam rangkaian penyambutan resmi Perdana Menteri (PM) Australia Anthony Albanese, di Istana Kepresidenan Bogor, Jawa Barat, pada Senin, 6 Juni 2022. Usai melakukan kegiatan penanaman pohon, Presiden Joko Widodo mengajak PM Albanese untuk bersepeda pagi.|Dari Istana Kepresidenan Bogor, kedua pemimpin menaiki sepeda bambu menuju Resto Raasaa yang terletak di Kebun Raya Bogor. Selain karena cuaca yang sangat bersahabat untuk bersepeda pagi, Presiden Jokowi mengatakan bahwa sepeda juga merupakan moda kendaraan ramah lingkungan.|"Karena cuacanya bagus dan naik sepeda ini kan ramah lingkungan, saya kira kita harus memulai menyampaikan pesan betapa pentingnya kendaraan-kendaraan yang ramah lingkungan. Kemudian yang ketiga, ini memang rute yang biasa saya pakai untuk olahraga," ujar Presiden Jokowi dalam keterangannya di Resto Raasaa, Kebun Raya Bogor.|Sementara itu, PM Albanese mengaku bahwa pengalaman bersepeda tersebut adalah pengalaman yang luar biasa dan menganggapnya sebagai sebuah kehormatan besar.|"Selamat pagi, itu adalah pengalaman yang luar biasa dan saya menganggap sebagai kehormatan besar bahwa Presiden mengundang saya untuk naik sepeda bambu bersamanya ke tempat yang indah di taman botani ini," ujar PM Albanese.|Lebih lanjut, PM Albanese memandang bahwa kegiatan bersepeda tersebut juga menunjukkan persahabatan antara Australia dan Indonesia. Menurutnya, Presiden Jokowi bahkan menawarkan agar sepeda bambunya dibawa ke Australia.|"Presiden telah menawarkan kepada saya untuk membawa sepeda itu kembali ke Australia dan Anda akan melihat saya mengendarai sepeda bambu satu-satunya di Canberra. Tapi itu adalah pengalaman yang luar biasa dan setiap kali saya naik sepeda, saya akan ingat persahabatan dengan Presiden Widodo," tuturnya.|Untuk diketahui, Presiden Jokowi dan PM Albanese menggunakan sepeda bambu yang dirancang untuk digunakan di jalan raya. Sepeda tersebut merupakan hasil karya Singgih S. Kartono dari Kabupaten Temanggung, Provinsi Jawa Tengah.|Usai bersepeda, kedua pemimpin kemudian menggelar pembicaraan tete-a-tete di area taman batu putih Resto Raasaa, Kebun Raya Bogor. Selama sekitar 30 menit keduanya terlibat perbincangan hangat sebelum kembali ke Istana Kepresidenan Bogor dengan menggunakan mobil golf untuk melakukan pertemuan bilateral kedua negara. |Bogor, 6 Juni 2022|Biro Pers, Media, dan Informasi Sekretariat Presiden|Website: https://www.presidenri.go.id|YouTube: Sekretariat Presiden

title: Koalisi Indonesia Bersatu Bangun Kekuatan untuk Pilpres, Gun Gun Heryanto : Ini Langkah Cantik
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Suhu politik 2 tahun jelang pemilu dan dan Pilpres 2024 terus menghangat.||||Beberapa hari lalu, Koalisi Indonesia Bersatu, KIB yang terdiri dari Golkar, Pan dan PPP menggelar konsolidasi perdana berupa silaturahmi nasional.||||Ketua Umum dari tiga partai itu menandatangani nota kesepahaman terbentuknya Koalisi Indonesia Bersatu.||||KIB belum bicara soal capres, tetapi berharap pilpres nanti diikuti sedikitnya tiga pasangan calon.||||Baca Juga Gelar Silatnas di Senayan, KIB Undang Relawan Pro-Jokowi Sebagai Bentuk Pertemanan di https://www.kompas.tv/article/295817/gelar-silatnas-di-senayan-kib-undang-relawan-pro-jokowi-sebagai-bentuk-pertemanan||||Relawan Pro Jokowi atau Projo, hadir dalam silaturahmi yang digelar Koalisi Indonesia Bersatu.||||Jika bicara soal capres, Projo menegaskan ojo kesusu atau jangan terburu-buru.||||Terbentuknya Koalisi Indonesia Bersatu mendapat tanggapan dari PDI- Perjuangan.||||PDIP menilai terbentuknya KIB ini sebagai bagian dari dinamika politik.||||Apalagi sampai saat ini belum ada partai politik yang mendeklarasikan tokoh pada pemilu 2024 mendatang.||||Pengamat politik dari Universitas Al Azhar Indonesia, Ujang Komarudin melihat kehadiran relawan Projo di Silatnas Koalisi Indonesia Bersatu kemarin, merupakan simbol bagi KIB yang ingin mendapatkan restu dari Presiden Joko Widodo.||||Selain itu, Ujang menilai silaturahim nasional KIB juga bertujuan untuk menaikkan posisi tawar poros politik KIB.||||Kekuatan Koalisi Indonesia bersatu memang cukup untuk mengusung capres cawapres atau presidential treshold.||||Dilihat dari perolehan suara pemilu 2019 lalu, Golkar mendapat 12,31%, pan: 6,84%, PPP: 4,52%  dengan total suara 23,67 persen.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296077/koalisi-indonesia-bersatu-bangun-kekuatan-untuk-pilpres-gun-gun-heryanto-ini-langkah-cantik

description: MAGELANG, KOMPAS.TV - Pemerintah berencana membatasi orang naik ke Candi Borobudur.||||Menurut rencana tarif naik ke Stupa Borobudur Rp750 ribu per orang untuk wisatawan lokal.||||Pembatasan jumlah pengunjung dilakukan agar kondisi Candi Borobudur sebagai cagar budaya tetap lestari. ||||Pembatasan dilakukan berdasarkan rekomendasi dari UNESCO serta para pakar bahwa Candi Borobudur sudah mengalami penurunan.||||Jumlah wisatawan nantinya dibatasi 1.200 orang per hari.||||Baca Juga Heboh Tarif Naik Candi Borobudur Rp750 Ribu, Luhut Tegaskan Belum Final dan Masih Dapat Turun di https://www.kompas.tv/article/295964/heboh-tarif-naik-candi-borobudur-rp750-ribu-luhut-tegaskan-belum-final-dan-masih-dapat-turun||||Berdasarkan situs borobudurpark.com, saat ini harga tiket masuk Candi Borobudur bagi wisatawan lokal dipatok sebesar Rp50 ribu rupiah untuk usia di atas 10 tahun.||||Dan anak usia 3 hingga 10 tahun dikenakan tarif masuk Rp25 ribu.||||Sementara harga tiket masuk untuk rombongan minimal 20 pelajar dan mahasiswa sebesar Rp25 ribu per orang.||||Sedangkan harga tiket masuk Candi Borobudur untuk wisatawan asing dewasa sebesar Rp350 ribu dan Rp210 ribu bagi turis asing anak-anak.||||Rencana kenaikan harga tiket Candi Borobudur, menimbulkan beragam tanggapan oleh para pengunjung.||||Ada wisatawan yang setuju dengan wacana ini, karena untuk menjaga kelestarian Candi Borobudur.||||Tetapi sebagian lainnya menilai, kenaikan tiket menjadi Rp750 ribu sangat memberatkan wisatawan lokal.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296018/tiket-naik-ke-stupa-borobudur-akan-naik-jadi-rp750-ribu-ini-tanggapan-para-pengunjung
tags: candi borobudur|harga tiket masuk candi|luhut|pembatasan pengunjung borobudur|stupa|unesco

title: Editorial View: Buntut Panjang Politik 'Ojo Kesusu' Jokowi
description: Hubungan Presiden Joko Widodo dengan Ketua Umum PDI Perjuangan, Megawati Soekarnoputri disebut-sebut makin renggang. Hal ini dipicu pernyataan Jokowi ketika menghadiri acara pendukungnya, Projo, di Magelang, Jawa Tengah, akhir Mei lalu. Ia tersirat mendukung Ganjar Pranowo, Gubernur Jawa Tengah, menjadi Calon Presiden 2024. Iqbal Kurniadi membahasnya dalam wawancara via zoom bersama Revolusi Riza selaku Wakil Pemimpin Redaksi CNN Indonesia Dan Budi Setyarso selaku Kepala Pemberitaan Korporat Tempo
tags: politik|jokowi|ojo kesusu

title: Aksi Arogansi Pengemudi Mobil Berpelat RFH, Sekjen PDIP Minta Polisi Tindak Tegas Pelaku
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Aksi arogansi pengemudi mobil kembali terjadi di jalanan Kota Jakarta.||||Kali ini pengemudi mobil berpelat nomor RFH melakukan penganiayaan kepada pengendara mobil lainnya.||||Kami sengaja menyamarkan video ini karena mengandung unsur kekesaran.||||Dalam video yang direkam oleh pengguna jalan Tol Dalam Kota Jakarta ini, terlihat seorang pria melakukan penganiayaan kepada pengendara mobil lainnya.||||Setelah korban melapor, polisi langsung menangkap kedua pengemudi mobil RFH untuk diperiksa.||||Polisi membenarkan dua pelaku penganiayaan di Tol Dalam Kota yang ada dalam video, telah ditangkap.||||Baca Juga 5 Fakta Dugaan Penganiayaan oleh Seorang Pengendara Kendaraan Pelat RFH di Tol Dalam Kota DKI di https://www.kompas.tv/article/295839/5-fakta-dugaan-penganiayaan-oleh-seorang-pengendara-kendaraan-pelat-rfh-di-tol-dalam-kota-dki||||Saat ini, keduanya masih dalam pemeriksaan.||||Tidak sedikit warga yang menganggap pengemudi arogan meresahkan.||||Mereka berharap kepada para pengemudi untuk lebih dapat menahan emosi mereka selama berkendara, mengingat saat ini kemacetan di beberapa titik kembali terjadi.||||Hal ini juga dapat membahayakan keselamatan pengemudi di jalan.||||Diketahui korban penganiayaan di jalan tol, adalah putra anggota DPR RI, Fraksi PDI-P Indah Kurniawati.||||Sekjen PDI Perjuangan, Hasto Kristiyanto pun meminta agar tindakan main hakim sendiri, ditindak tegas karena melanggar aturan yang berlaku di Indonesia.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296010/aksi-arogansi-pengemudi-mobil-berpelat-rfh-sekjen-pdip-minta-polisi-tindak-tegas-pelaku
tags: anak dpr|indah kurniawati|mobil plat rfh|penganiayaan|sekjen pdip|tol dalam kota

title: At Least 50 Dead After Nigeria Church Attack

title: Global National: June 5, 2022 | Queenâ€™s Platinum Jubilee celebrations end with colourful pageant
description: On this episode of Global National: It was a pageant fit for a queen. From essential workers to celebrities, some 10,000 people made their way to Buckingham Palace on Sunday to pay tribute Queen Elizabeth II. The festivities, honouring the monarchâ€™s seven decades of service, culminated with a surprise appearance by the Queen on the balcony of Buckingham Palace. Redmond Shannon reports. |The city of London, Ont., marked a tragic anniversary on Sunday. It was one year ago that four members of a Muslim family were killed when they were hit by a truck in what police and prosecutors describe as a hate-motivated crime. Only the youngest child survived. Abigail Bimman looks at how the community is honouring their memory.|There is now a clear picture of how many crises the international community is ignoring. The Norwegian Refugee Council, a humanitarian organization, has released its annual â€œTop 10â€ list of the most neglected crises around the world and for the first time all 10 are in Africa. Mike Armstrong is in the Democratic Republic of Congo, a country sitting at the top of that grim ranking.|There is no denying that Queen Elizabeth has been an enduring presence in the world. title: Kekasih Eril Tulis Pesan Menyentuh Disosmed, Opie Kumis Ungkap Ini Tentang Sosok Anak Ridwan Kamil
description: For Business Inquiries/Endorsement contact : business@creativeindigo.net|Kumpulan video berita gosip terlengkap, terhangat dan terbaru hari ini seputar selebritis Indonesia|Langsung aja klik http://www.cumicumi.com/|#opiekumis #eril #cumicumi |---|---|Kesedihan tidak hanya dirasakan oleh Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil dan pihak keluarganya yang telah  mengikhlaskan kepergian Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau yang kerap disapa Eril, tetapi juga hampir semua lapisan masyrakat. Tidak terkecuali dari kalangan selebriti yang turut berduka atas meniggalnya Eril. Salah satu yang turut berduka atas kepergian Eril ialah komedian Opie Kumis yang mengaku mempunyai pengalaman tersendiri dengan putra sulung Ridwan Kamil itu. Opie Kumis menuturkan jika Eril merupakan sosok yang sangat baik dan sopan kepada siapa aja yang ditemuinya. title: Jennifer Lopez CRIES & Shouts Out Ben Affleck In Personal MTV Awards Speech
description: Jennifer Lopez left it all on the stage at the 2022 MTV Movie & TV Awards! The superstar received this year's Generation Award and accepted the honor with an emotional speech that brought her to tears. JLo thanked her kids, fans and longtime manager Benny Medina for helping her reach her dreams, and she became overcome with emotion when reflecting on the love and support she has around her.

title: Pengamat: Orang Melihat Formula E Panggung Anies Baswedan
description: Sebagai ajang olahraga balap mobil, Formula E kental dengan nuansa politik. Mulai dari proses persiapan hingga usai pelaksanaannya masih menyisakan perbincangan politik terkait gelaran mobil listrik itu. Sempat memanas pada beberapa hari jelang acara karena dianggap bumn tidak mendukung secara finansial maupun moral, presiden joko widodo pun hadir dan duduk bersama gubernur anies baswedan serta beberapa tokoh politik di tribun penonton pada hari H. Bagaimana membaca anasir dan simbol-simbol komunikasi politik pada peristiwa Formula E? Dea Kartika membahasnya dalam wawancara via zoom bersama Nyarwi Ahmad selaku Analis Komunikasi Politik UGM.

title: Bravo 5 Ungkap Pemicu Pemukulan di Jalan Tol yang Libatkan Ali Fanser: JF Acungkan Jari Tengah
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS TV  Pihak ormas Pejuang Pemuda Bravo Lima buka suara perihal viral pemukulan anak anggota DPR RI oleh pria dari mobil dengan pelat RFH.||||Sekretaris Pejuang Pemuda Bravo Lima membenarkan bahwa yang ada dalam video adalah Ketua Umum Pemuda Bravo Lima yaitu Ali Fanser Marasabessy.||||Namun, Ali Fanser tidak melakukan pemukulan, melainkan ingin melerai anaknya yang tengah melakukan pemukulan pada Justin Frederick.||||Baca Juga Ada Perbedaan Kronologi dari Korban dan Pelaku Arogansi Mobil Plat RFH di Tol Dalam Kota di https://www.kompas.tv/article/295975/ada-perbedaan-kronologi-dari-korban-dan-pelaku-arogansi-mobil-plat-rfh-di-tol-dalam-kota||||"Tidak benar teman kami Ali Fanser melakukan pemukulan. Bahkan, terlihat dalam video beliau tidak melakukan pemukulan. Beliau bahkan berupaya untuk melerai," ungkap Sekretaris Pejuang Pemuda Bravo Lima Ahmad Zazali.||||"Namanya juga anak melihat orangtuanya dipukul, maka anak melakukan pembelaan pada anaknya.||||Di kesempatan yang sama Zazali ungkap kronologi sebelum terjadinya pemukulan anak Ali Fanser pada Justin Frederick.||||Ia menyebut bahwa Justin terlebih dahulu melakukan provokasi dengan mengacungkan jari tengah, bahkan memukul terlebih dahulu.||||"Rekan kami dua orang ini memotong mobil, dan dia memberi tanda jari tengah" ujar Zazali.||||"JF emosi meledak-ledak dan sempat memukul terlebih dahulu kepada bang Ali Fanser" lanjutnya.||||Sebuah video viral memperlihatkan seorang pemuda dianiaya oleh seorang yang keluar dari mobil dengan akhiran pelat RFH.||||Setelah ditelusuri, ternyata korban pemukulan merupakan anak dari anggota DPR RI, sementara salah satu orang dari mobil RFH adalah ketua umum ormas Pemuda Bravo Lima.||||Video Editor: Laurensius Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/296008/bravo-5-ungkap-pemicu-pemukulan-di-jalan-tol-yang-libatkan-ali-fanser-jf-acungkan-jari-tengah

title: Mark Cuban aims to lower prescription drug prices with online pharmacy
description: People searching for cheaper alternatives to high priced prescription drugs have a new and perhaps unexpected option. It's an online pharmacy founded by Mark Cuban, a billionaire businessman, Shark Tank star and owner of the Dallas Mavericks. His new direct-to-consumer company, Cost Plus Drugs, offers more than 100 generic medications at discounted prices. title: Billy Horschel wins 7th PGA TOUR title | Round 4 | the Memorial | 2022
description: In the final round of the Memorial Tournament presented by Workday 2022, Billy Horschel carded an even-par 72, and at 13-under after 72 holes, won his seventh PGA TOUR title by four shots.|SUBSCRIBE to PGA TOUR now: http://pgat.us/vBxcZSh||||This week, the PGA TOUR heads to Muirfield Village Golf Club for the Memorial Tournament presented by Workday. Reigning FedExCup champion Patrick Cantlay returns to defend his title as seven of the top-10 players in the Official World Golf Ranking are all set to tee it up. Collin Morikawa, who lost to Patrick Cantlay in a playoff in 2021, will be looking for his first victory of the PGA TOUR season. After a strong start to the year, the American has finished outside the top 20 in his last three tournaments. While Jon Rahm returns as a past winner, world No. 3 Cam Smith will be hoping to claim his third title of the year after winning the Sentry Tournament of Champions and THE PLAYERS Championship. Viktor Hovland, Rory McIlroy and Jordan Spieth are the other top-10 players in the field in Dublin, Ohio. Sponsor exemptions include Jason Day, Rickie Fowler and Brandt Snedeker.||||Check out https://www.pgatour.com for complete coverage along with all the latest news, scoring, and stats!||||Follow PGA TOUR online:||Instagram: https://instagram.com/pgatour/  ||Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PGATour  ||Twitter: https://twitter.com/PGATOUR||TikTok: https://tiktok.com/@pgatour||SoundCloud: https://soundcloud.com/pgatour||||Sign up for exclusive coverage - http://www.pgatourlive.com||PGA TOUR Superstore - http://www.pgatoursuperstore.com/

title: Highlights | Round 4 | the Memorial | 2022
description: Check out the best shots of the day from Round 4 at the Memorial Tournament presented by Workday 2022, featuring Billy Horshel, Aaron Wise, Patrick Cantlay and Joaquin Niemann among others.|SUBSCRIBE to PGA TOUR now: http://pgat.us/vBxcZSh||||This week, the PGA TOUR heads to Muirfield Village Golf Club for the Memorial Tournament presented by Workday. Reigning FedExCup champion Patrick Cantlay returns to defend his title as seven of the top-10 players in the Official World Golf Ranking are all set to tee it up. Collin Morikawa, who lost to Patrick Cantlay in a playoff in 2021, will be looking for his first victory of the PGA TOUR season. After a strong start to the year, the American has finished outside the top 20 in his last three tournaments. While Jon Rahm returns as a past winner, world No. 3 Cam Smith will be hoping to claim his third title of the year after winning the Sentry Tournament of Champions and THE PLAYERS Championship. Viktor Hovland, Rory McIlroy and Jordan Spieth are the other top-10 players in the field in Dublin, Ohio. title: Ridwan Kamil Kenang Eril, Sebut Sang Anak Tak Senang Jika Kebaikan Diceritakan
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS TV  Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil unggah sebuah tulisan di Instagram, yang berisi kesaksiannya tentang hidup sang anak, Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril.||||Dalam unggahan tersebut, Ridwan Kamil malah menyebut sebetulnya sang anak akan tidak terlalu senang jika amal dan kebaikannya diceritakan.||||"Izinkan saya selaku ayahanda Eril, untuk memberi kesaksian atas kiprah dan semangat hidupnya selama ini," tulis Ridwan Kamil.||||Baca Juga Pilu Ridwan Kamil untuk Eril: Seandainya Kami Bisa Bertukar Tempat... di https://www.kompas.tv/article/295990/pilu-ridwan-kamil-untuk-eril-seandainya-kami-bisa-bertukar-tempat||||"Saya tahu betul, Eril jika masih ada, pasti tidak terlalu senang jika amal atau kebaikannya diceritakan," lanjutnya.||||Ia pun menulis sebuah tulisan yang mengisakan masa-masa hidup sang anak.||||"Kisah tentang Eril, anak lelaku kesayangan kami, hakekatnya adalah cerita tentang kita semua. Hakekat bahwa semua dari kita, pasti akan pulang. Dengan waktu, tempat dan cara yang kita tidak akan pernah selalu tahu," tulis RK.||||"Hidup di dunia ini sesungguhnya adalah tentang perjalanan bukan tujuan. Dan seperti cerita setiap perjalanan, kisah selalu dimulai dari sebuah titik awal. Dan kisah akan selesai di sebuah titik akhir. Dan untuk setiap yang datang, pasti aka nada saatnya untuk kembali pulang," lanjutnya.||||Hal tersebut RK unggah setelah ia dan keluarga menyatakan ikhlas dan meyakini Eril wafat atau meninggal dunia tenggelam di Sungai Aare, Swiss.||||Ridwan Kamil dan keluarga pun telah gelar doa bersama untuk kepergian Eril.||||Video Editor: Laurensius Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/295992/ridwan-kamil-kenang-eril-sebut-sang-anak-tak-senang-jika-kebaikan-diceritakan
tags: emmeril kahn mumtadz|eril meninggal dunia|instagram ridwan kamil|ridwan kamil eril|ridwan kamil tentang eril

title: Editorial View: Tensi Tinggi Politik Formula E
description: Setelah 2 tahun tertunda, gelaran Formula E Jakarta 2022 akhirnya telah terlaksana. Penyelenggaraannya pun dianggap sukses. Bahkan Presiden Jokowi mengatakan, ajang bergengsi yang berlangsung di Jakarta International E-Prix Circuit ini berjalan lancar.|Namun tetap saja, di belakangnya tak sedikit drama yang menyertai. Mulai dari pro kontra pembangunan sirkuit, bergulirnya hak interpelasi di DPRD DKI Jakarta, pandemi, hingga sponsor acara. Lalu bagaimana perspektif media melihat ajang ini? Iqbal Kurniadi membahasnya dalam wawancara via zoom bersama Revolusi Riza selaku Wakil Pemimpin Redaksi CNN Indonesia Dan Budi Setyarso selaku Kepala Pemberitaan Korporat Tempo.
tags: formula e|politik|tensi tinggi

title: News Wrap: Russian airstrikes target Kyiv, interrupting weeks of calm

title: Qatar, Kuwait, Iran summon Indian envoys over BJP leader's Prophet remark; Watch Indiaâ€™s response
description: Indian envoys in Qatar, Kuwait & Iran were summoned over the suspended BJP leader's remark on Prophet Mohammad. Indian envoy handed an official note to Qatar minister of state for foreign affairs Soltan Bin Saad Al-Muraikhi. Kuwait's deputy foreign minister for Asia slammed the 'abusive statementsâ€™ against the Prophet. Iran, too, has summoned the Indian Ambassadors to Tehran over the issue. title: Ganjar Pranowo Dapat Dukungan dari 30 Ribu Relawan Des Ganjar untuk Jadi Presiden di 2024
description: JEPARA, KOMPAS.TV - Sebanyak 30 ribu masyarakat desa yang mengatas namakan Des Ganjar, dari 32 provinsi seluruh Indonesia mendeklarasikan dukungannya kepada Ganjar Pranowo untuk menjadi Presiden 2024.||||Deklarasi digelar di kawasan Pantai Bandengan, Jepara, Jawa Tengah.||||Menurut Deklarator Nasional Des Ganjar, Ulil Albab, Ganjar adalah sosok yang pantas untuk menjadi Presiden.||||Baca Juga Hasil Survei SMRC, Pendukung Jokowi pada 2019 Cenderung Pilih Ganjar Maju Pilpres 2024 di https://www.kompas.tv/article/295818/hasil-survei-smrc-pendukung-jokowi-pada-2019-cenderung-pilih-ganjar-maju-pilpres-2024||||Sementara itu, Ketua Des Ganjar Jawa Tengah, Hartoyo menambahkan, Ganjar juga dinilai sangat peduli kepada masyarakat.||||Sebelumnya, deklarasi Des Ganjar tidak hanya dilakukan di Jawa Tengah, namun juga telah dilakukan di 14 provinsi di seluruh Indonesia untuk mengenalkan sosok Ganjar Pranowo menuju Presiden 2024.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/295974/ganjar-pranowo-dapat-dukungan-dari-30-ribu-relawan-des-ganjar-untuk-jadi-presiden-di-2024

title: Nigeria: Gunmen opened fire on worshippers in Catholic church, killing dozens | DW News
description: Gunmen have killed dozens of worshippers in a Catholic church in southwestern Nigeria, Ondo state governor said on Sunday. |The assailants stormed the church in the midst of the Sunday service, opening fire at the worshippers, local media reported. Some explosives were also used, but initial reports suggest the majority of injuries were due to gunshots. |The identities of the perpetrators, who fled the scene shortly after the attack, have yet to be confirmed. Local reports have pointed the finger at Fulani Herdsmen, suggesting members of the nomadic group carried out the attack to send a message to the governor.|#Nigeria #Church #Attack|Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch

title: Putin warns of Russia hitting new targets if US gives missiles to Ukraine | DW News
description: Russian President Vladimir Putin said Moscow will respond to the West delivering long-range missiles to Ukraine. |His remarks come after the US pledged to supply Kyiv with M142 systems armed with precisions-guided missiles. The range of the missiles, according to media reports, would be between 70 to 80 kilometers (43.5 to 50 miles).|In comments broadcast on Sunday, Putin said the systems were "nothing new" and their range depended on the missiles that the US decided to provide.|"But, if they will be delivered, we will draw appropriate conclusions and use our own weapons, of which we have enough, to strike objects that we haven't struck before," Putin told Russia's state broadcaster. |The Russian president did not specify which targets he had in mind.|#Ukraine #Russia #VladimirPutin|Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch

title: Qatar, Kuwait and Now Iran - Prophet Controversy Snowballs
description: Two BJP leaders' comments on Prophet Muhammad have unleashed a backlash in Islamic nations, with Qatar, Kuwait and Iran summoning the Indian envoy today. On social media there have been calls to ban Indian products. Qatar told India envoy Deepak Mittal that "Allowing such Islamophobic remarks to continue without punishment, constitutes a grave danger to the protection of human rights and may lead to further prejudice and marginalization, which will create a cycle of violence and hate". Kuwait demanded a "public apology for these hostile statements, the continuation of which would constitute a deterrent measure or punishment to increase extremism and hatred and undermine the elements of moderation".'|About NDTV: NDTV brings you unbiased and comprehensive coverage of news and entertainment programmes in India and abroad. title: Ada Perbedaan Kronologi dari Korban dan Pelaku Arogansi Mobil Plat RFH di Tol Dalam Kota
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Aksi arogansi pengemudi mobil kembali terjadi di jalanan Kota Jakarta.||||Kali ini pengemudi mobil berpelat nomor RFH melakukan penganiayaan kepada pengendara mobil lainnya.||||Kami sengaja menyamarkan video ini karena mengandung unsur kekesaran.||||Dalam video yang direkam oleh pengguna jalan Tol Dalam Kota Jakarta ini, terlihat seorang pria melakukan penganiayaan kepada pengendara mobil lainnya.||||Setelah korban melapor, polisi langsung menangkap kedua pengemudi mobil RFH untuk diperiksa.||||Polisi membenarkan dua pelaku penganiayaan di Tol Dalam Kota yang ada dalam video, telah ditangkap.||||Saat ini, keduanya masih dalam pemeriksaan.||||Korban penganiayaan diketahui merupakan anak dari anggota DPR Komisi XI fraksi PDI-P, Indah Kurnia.||||Orang tua korban sangat menyayangkan aksi arogansi yang dilakukan oleh pelaku.||||Korban pun meminta polisi untuk menindak tegas pelaku sesuai dengan peraturan yang berlaku.||||Sekjen PDI Perjuangan, Hasto Kristiyanto pun meminta, agar tindakan main hakim sendiri, ditindak tegas, karena melanggar aturan yang berlaku di Indonesia.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/295975/ada-perbedaan-kronologi-dari-korban-dan-pelaku-arogansi-mobil-plat-rfh-di-tol-dalam-kota

title: BJP Leaders Removed Over Prophet Remarks: Party's Damage Control? | Left, Right & Centre
description: Two BJP leaders' comments on Prophet Muhammad have unleashed a backlash in Islamic nations, with Qatar, Kuwait and Iran summoning the Indian envoy today. On social media there have been calls to ban Indian products. The two BJP spokespersons have been suspended by the BJP. Why this about turn? Is this because there is a recognition that the communal stress that we have seen in India over the last few months has now reached a tipping point or is there an understanding that crucial strategic relationships with some of our closest partners could end up being demolished at the altar of so called TV debate shows. description: The Queen's Platinum Jubilee Weekend draws to a close with iconic moments from Her Majesty's 70-year reign brought to life by a cast of thousands in The Platinum Pageant. Watching along in the royal box were the Prince of Wales and the Duchess of Cornwall with Princess Anne alongside the Duke and Duchess of Cambridge and their children. Prince Louis kept crowds entertained with his excitement and reactions to the colour-filled procession. |. Report by Louis Etemadi.

title: Queen's Platinum Jubilee: Pageant celebrates Queen Elizabeth's 70 years on the throne  | FULL
description: Festivities celebrating Queen Elizabeth's 70 years on the throne wrapped up on Sunday with the Platinum Jubilee Pageant, which tells the story of her reign in four parts. |The pageant opened with a military spectacle, honouring the U.K. armed forces from across the Commonwealth, including Canada, New Zealand, Australia, Pakistan, Ghana  and Belize among others. A hologram of the queen during her coronation in 1953 was also broadcast on the windows of the Gold State Coach, waving to the crowds as the carriage went by. |The pageant then showcased British life and spirit since 1952, when she acceded to the throne following her father's death.|According to the program for the event, the third act harnessed "creativity, ingenuity, humour and community spirit," and will include the "very best" of Carnival, May Day, Mela, Fiesta and Mardi Gras to celebrate the Queen's life experience. |The procession then ended at the Queen Victoria Memorial in front of Buckingham Palace. The monarch surprised attendees by walking out onto the balcony of the palace with members of her family to wave at the crowds. |For more info, please go to https://globalnews.ca/news/8894423/future-kings-queen-elizabeth-jubilee-concert/|Subscribe to Global News Channel HERE: http://bit.ly/20fcXDc|Like Global News on Facebook HERE: http://bit.ly/255GMJQ|Follow Global News on Twitter HERE: http://bit.ly/1Toz8mt|Follow Global News on Instagram HERE: https://bit.ly/2QZaZIB|#GlobalNews

title: Scientist who predicted Boxing Day tsunami says another disaster is coming | 60 Minutes Australia

title: Why The World Is Running Out Of Soil
description: Critical topsoil is eroding at an alarming pace due to climate change and poor farming practices. The United Nations declared soil finite and predicted catastrophic loss within 60 years. The world needs soil for farming, water filtration, climate mitigation, ecosystem services, health care and more. The impact of soil degradation could total $23 trillion in losses of food, ecosystem services and income worldwide by 2050, according to the United Nations Convention to Combat Desertification. According to the UN, soil erosion may reduce up to 10 per cent of crop yields by 2050. Thatâ€™s like removing millions of acres of farm land. |â€œThere are places that have already lost all of their topsoil,â€ Jo Handelsman, author of â€œA World Without Soil,â€ and a professor at the University of Wisconsin-Madison, told CNBC.|â€œWe have identified 10 soil threats in our global report â€¦ Soil erosion is number one because itâ€™s taking place everywhere,â€ Ronald Vargas, the secretary of the Global Soil Partnership and Land and Water Officer at the Food and Agriculture Organization of the United Nations, told CNBC.|According to the U.N., soil erosion may reduce up to 10% of crop yields by 2050, which is the equivalent of removing millions of acres of farmland.|And when the world loses soil, food supply, clean drinking water and biodiversity are threatened.|Whatâ€™s more, soil plays an important role in mitigating climate change.|Soil contains more than three times the amount of carbon in the earthâ€™s atmosphere and four times as much in all living plants and animals combined, according to the Columbia Climate School.| â€œSoil is the habitat for over a quarter of the planetâ€™s biodiversity. Each gram of soil contains millions of cells of bacteria and fungi that play a very important role in all ecosystem services,â€ Reza Afshar, chief scientist at the regenerative agriculture research farm at the Rodale Institute, told CNBC.|The Rodale Institute in Kutztown, Pennsylvania, is known as the birthplace of modern organic agriculture. |â€œThe projects we do here are centered around improving and rebuilding soil health. We have a farming system trial thatâ€™s been running for 42 years,â€ Afshar said. It is the longest-running side-by-side comparison of organic and conventional grain cropping systems in North America.|The research has found regenerative, organic agriculture produces yields up to 40% higher during droughts, can earn farmers greater profits and releases 40% fewer carbon emissions than conventional agricultural practices.|Howâ€™s that possible? The Rodale Institute says it all starts with the soil.|â€œWhen we talk about healthy soil, we are talking about all aspects of the soil, chemical, physical and biological that should be in a perfect status to be able to produce healthy food for us,â€ Afshar said.|Itâ€™s critical, of course, because the world relies on soil for 95% of our food production. But thatâ€™s just the beginning of its importance.|â€œThe good news is that we know enough to get to work,â€ Dianna Bagnall, a research soil scientist at the Soil Health Institute, told CNBC.|Watch the video above to learn more about why weâ€™re facing a silent soil crisis, how soil can be saved and what that means for the world.|Â» Subscribe to CNBC: https://cnb.cx/SubscribeCNBC|Â» Subscribe to CNBC TV: https://cnb.cx/SubscribeCNBCtelevision|Â» Subscribe to CNBC Classic: https://cnb.cx/SubscribeCNBCclassic|About CNBC: From 'Wall Street' to 'Main Street' to award winning original documentaries and Reality TV series, CNBC has you covered. title: Stranger Things Season 4 Behind The Scenes
description: Season 4 of Stranger Things has really upped the ante, and proved itself as one of the show's best seasons. Creating a show as big as Stranger Things is no easy task. There was a lot of work going on behind the scenes to bring the show to life. Between recreating Southern California in another state, to coordinating massive scenes with crazy stunts, everyone gave a hundred and ten percent to help create this season. That being said, there was also a lot of goofing off and shenanigans between the cast members. Millie Bobby Brown and Noah Schnaap in particular had a lot of hilarious stories about their on set experiences while filming. Can you guess which one of them got pelted by water balloons?|Creating the right look and aesthetic was extremely important for the Stranger Things team. Vecna is one of the coolest monsters we have seen on the show, and a ton of hard work went into creating his look. The prosthetics team had their hands full, as they applied a whopping amount of prosthetics. Itâ€™s almost hard to believe how many individual pieces were applied to actor Jamie Campbell. Itâ€™s no wonder he spent so long in the makeup chair!|Sometimes the best behind the scenes moments have nothing to do with the show, and come purely from the chemistry all the actors have with each other. Like which cast members competed in a fruit by the foot challenge?|Which behind the scenes moment from Stranger Things season 4 is your favorite? title: The Truth About My Fight "Controversy" w/ iDubbbz
description: In May I was lucky enough to be invited to Tampa, Florida to compete in the first ever "Creator Clash", an influencer boxing event designed to raise money for charity. Together with the other fighters we raised over 1.3 million dollars! It was a life-changing experience to not only compete but watch my fellow YouTubers fight as well, such as Michael Reeves, Harley from Epic Meal Time, Graham Stephan, Alex Ernst, Justamix, Hundar, AB from the H3 podcast, Dad and Mat Watson, James from TheOdd1sOut, and so many more. While this event was an incredible success and couldn't possibly be overshadowed by anything, it didn't come without its controversies. Today I want to give you a behind the scenes look at my time in Tampa and everything surrounding my main event fight with Creator Clash creator, iDubbbz. If you followed the event at all then you may already know about the mix up with rounds and their lengths, the anger towards my glove tap in the second round, or any of the other drama that's been discussed on reddit forums and podcasts across YouTube. title: Plot Twist: Hubble Just Confirmed Our Physics Is Broken
description: With the first images of the James Webb Space Telescope around the corner, the iconic Hubble Space Telescope has made an important discovery. Three decades of data show that the universe is expanding faster than we predict, which means that something is seriously wrong with our cosmology models. Accurate determination of the Hubble constant has been one of the fundamental goals in cosmology for the past hundred years. Different methods have been used to find the value of the Hubble constant observational and theoretically. But each measurement has added more to the confusion than clearing things up.|The tenth episode of the Sunday Discoveries Series talks about the recent evaluation of the Hubble constant by the Hubble Space Telescope.|All Episodes Of The Series: https://bit.ly/369kG4p|Basics of Astrophysics series: https://bit.ly/3xII54M|REFERENCES:|2022 Hubble Constant Research Paper: https://bit.ly/3GRCEXs|2022 Press Release: https://go.nasa.gov/3xiETQd|2019 Hubble Constant Research Paper: https://bit.ly/3MsrU36|2019 Press Release: https://bit.ly/3zjGqqW|Hubble's Law: https://bit.ly/3MlUbIu|CMB Radiation: https://bit.ly/3NrfWYD|The Day We Discovered The Universe: https://bit.ly/3MoByDA|Cepheids: https://bit.ly/3zjpSPR|Type 1a Supernovae: https://go.nasa.gov/3axCwAs|Created By: Rishabh Nakra|Written By: Simran Buttar|Narrated By: Jeffrey Smith|The Secrets of the Universe on the internet:|Website: https://bit.ly/sou_website|Facebook: https://bit.ly/sou_fb|Instagram: https://bit.ly/sou_ig|Twitter: https://bit.ly/sou_twitter

title: What leads mothers to kill their children? | DW Documentary (True crime documentary)
description: What could lead a loving mother like Carol Coronado to murder her children? Like hundreds of other new mothers who have killed their children or themselves, Coronado suffered from postpartum psychosis.|No one noticed, so no one was able to stop the tragedy from happening. With direct access to Carol Coronado's family and her lawyers, the film examines the taboo topic of maternal mental health, as well as a legal system marked by archaic laws and chronic levels of misunderstanding. Carol Coronado's story also brings to light serious problems within the health care system, many of which are seldom talked about.|The documentary follows the case of Carol Coronado in real-time, as her family and defense attorneys work to make sure she receives appropriate treatment, rather than simply being punished with the full force of the law. Sadly, postpartum depression and psychosis are becoming more common amid the isolation of the global pandemic, a situation that makes the film all the more urgent and moving.|#documentary #dwdocumentary #truecrime|______|DW Documentary gives you knowledge beyond the headlines. title: Tom Cruise v. Christopher Nolan: The Battle for the Best IMAX Stunts
description: For over a decade, Tom Cruise and Christopher Nolan have been creating some of the best IMAX movies by conjuring up some of the best movie stunts ever and photographing them with the glorious clarity of 65mm IMAX cameras. From the truck flip in The Dark Knight to the HALO jump in Mission Impossible Fallout, we take a deep dive into how these filmmakers committed these crazy stunts to celluloid.   |Tom Cruise is back in the cockpit with Top Gun: Maverick. The sequel has some of the best dog fight scenes ever made. A big reason these scenes feel so genuine is that Tom Cruise and the other Top Gun 2 actors were actually filmed in real jet fighters pulling real Gs. Tom knows that a big Tom Cruise stunt is the main reason people go see Tom Cruise movies, but Tom Cruise isnâ€™t the only filmmaker out there filming crazy stunts for IMAX cameras. |Thereâ€™s also Christopher Nolan, who was the first filmmaker to really usher in this era of IMAX movies featuring crazy movie stunts. Of course we talk about Christopher Nolanâ€™s truck flip from The Dark Knight, his follow-up to Batman Begins. |If it wasnâ€™t for The Dark Knight, Tom Cruise might not have been motivated to make what is easily one of his top 5 action scenes of all time, the wall-running stunt on the Burj Khalifa.|Dangling from a building 2,700 ft up may seem like one of the craziest Tom Cruise stunts, but Christopher Nolan was ready to top it with the plane heist in The Dark Kngiht Rises. |We also talk about the plane stunt from Mission Impossible: Rogue Nation, the dog fights in Dunkirk, the HALO jump from Mission Impossible: Fallout, and the 747 crash in Tenet. All of these scenes can easily propel these movies make top 10 lists of best action movies, and theyâ€™re all the better because they were shot in IMAX.|So tune in and check out how Tom Cruise and Chris Nolan waged the battle for the Best IMAX Stunts.

title: Simplified Indonesian Chicken Fried Rice - Nasi Goreng
description: This version of Nasi Goreng is a simplified version that can be made as a quick 15-minute, chicken recipe with rice.  You will however need cooked rice from the day before.  If you wish to cook it from scratch, once cooked, I suggest cooling the rice down on a tray, then place it into a freezer for 20 minutes before using it.  This will prevent it from clumping together.  Fried rice however is always best with left over rice from the day before.  Always use it cold from fridge.| I just came back from Bali Indonesia where Nasi Goreng seems to be one of the most popular meals.  There are many versions of Indonesian Nasi Goreng, most have a more complex paste called â€œBase Genepâ€ where youâ€™ll usually find the addition of candlenut, galangal, ginger, lemon grass, birdâ€™s eye chilies, cumin, peppercorns, salam leaves and more.  Feel free to add any of those ingredients if you have them.  If you donâ€™t, no problem, this basic recipe will still deliver an amazing chicken fried rice everyone will love. |Another recipe30 cooking video inspired from travels.  See my travel vlogs.|ğŸ‘‰ Get this written recipe link here:  https://recipe30.com/chicken-fried-rice.html/|â–¶ Check out my favourite kitchen tools here (affiliate):  https://www.amazon.com/shop/recipe30  |â–¶ Follow me on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/recipe30/|â–¶ Follow me on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/recipe30/|â–¶Music by Epidemic Sound:  https://www.epidemicsound.com/referral/39ip8k|Want to mail me something? |Fan mail and products|MAILING ADDRESS:|RECIPE30|PO BOX 416|MOUNT MARTHA 3934|VICTORIA AUSTRALIA

title: Putin's men target Kyiv after weeks of calm; Brutal street fights intensify in Severodonetsk
description: After weeks of calm, multiple blasts rocked the Ukrainian capital today morning; at least one person hospitalised. Missile strikes on infrastructure come at a time when life had just begun inching towards normalcy in Kyiv. The Russians hit the Darnytskyi & Dniprovskyi districts of Kyiv, smoke continued long after the explosions. Kyivâ€™s Darnytskyi dist. sits on the left bank of the Dnipro, while the Dniprovskyi district lies along the river.|Dnipro river divides Ukraine between east & west - for some, the expanse has become a natural border with Russians. title: Kim Jong-Un test-fires 8 missiles in a day after U.S & South Korea joint military drill | Details
description: North Korea test-fires eight missiles in just a day pushing it to a record number of launches in a single year under Kim Jong Un, who appears ready to further ratchet up tensions with his first test of a nuclear device since 2017. The missiles were launched from multiple sites in North Korea into waters east of the Korean peninsula between 9:08 a.m. and 9:43 a.m. local time in Seoul on Sunday, according to the South Korean Joint Chiefs of Staff. The ballistic barrage took place just a day after South Korea and the United States wrapped up their joint military drill. North Korea has so far fired off 31 ballistic missiles in 2022, which include at least two failed attempts - the highest annual launches by the country ever. South Korea and Japan have slammed Kim Jong-Un's latest move. The United States too called it a violation of UNSC resolutions. Watch this report to know more.|#NorthKorea #KimJongUn #MissileLaunch #RecordBallisticBarrage

title: Stephanie Browitt's moment of triumph after White Island tragedy | 60 Minutes Australia
description: Subscribe here: http://9Soci.al/chmP50wA97J Full Episodes: https://9now.app.link/uNP4qBkmN6 | Facing the World (2022)|The pain Stefanie Browitt has endured defies description. When New Zealand's White Island volcano erupted in December 2019 she suffered horrific burns. Since then she's had dozens of excruciating surgeries and skin grafts, but for the 26-year-old, the greatest agony has been the loss of her dad and sister who were killed in the disaster. Throughout this awful time though, Steph has always tried to be optimistic, and tonight she wants to share a moment of triumph. That never-ending reminder of her injuries; the uncomfortable compression suits and masks she's had to be wrapped up in, are coming off. You're about to see why - inside and out - Stephanie Browitt is truly beautiful.|WATCH more of 60 Minutes Australia: https://www.60minutes.com.au |LIKE 60 Minutes Australia on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/60Minutes9 |FOLLOW 60 Minutes Australia on Twitter: https://twitter.com/60Mins |FOLLOW 60 Minutes Australia on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/60minutes9|For forty years, 60 Minutes have been telling Australians the worldâ€™s greatest stories. title: Sampaikan Dukacita Atas Meninggalnya Eril, Tangis Warga Pecah Saat Bertemu Ridwan Kamil dan Istri
description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS.TV - Duka masih menggelayut di Gedung Pakuan, Rumah Dinas Gubernur Jawa Barat, Ridwan Kamil.||||Dan di antara papan bunga ucapan belasungkawa, warga berdiri, berharap bisa mengikuti takziah mendoakan putra sulung Ridwan Kamil, mendiang Emmeril Kahn Mumtaz.||||Melihat besarnya simpati warga, untuk pertama kalinya pasca kehilangan putra sulungnya, Ridwan Kamil dan istri, Atalia, menemui warga.||||Baca Juga Temui Keluarga Ridwan Kamil, Dubes Palestina dan Wakil Ketua MPR Hadiri Doa Bersama untuk Eril di https://www.kompas.tv/article/295922/temui-keluarga-ridwan-kamil-dubes-palestina-dan-wakil-ketua-mpr-hadiri-doa-bersama-untuk-eril||||Dengan mengenakan baju hitam hitam, tanda duka tak terperi, Ridwan Kamil dan Atalia, menerima warga satu persatu. ||||Banyak tangis warga yang pecah, ikut bersedih atas meninggalnya Eril.||||Setelah 15 menit menemui warga, Ridwan Kamil dan istri kembali ke Gedung Pakuan.||||Untuk menyiapkan doa bersama bagi almarhum Eril pada pukul 13.00 WIB yang dibuka untuk umum dan dihadiri pejabat publik||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/295925/sampaikan-dukacita-atas-meninggalnya-eril-tangis-warga-pecah-saat-bertemu-ridwan-kamil-dan-istri

title: Moederskindje | Het Kantoor
description: De moeder van Wouter is op vakantie en nu moet Wouter helemaal voor zichzelf zorgen. description: Subscribe here: http://9Soci.al/chmP50wA97J Full Episodes: https://9now.app.link/uNP4qBkmN6 | Crypto Crash (2022)|It's the oldest saying in the book: What goes up must come down. In the volatile world of cryptocurrency, that's proving to be a brutal truth. Crypto's market value has halved since its peak late last year, haemorrhaging an eye watering $2.2 trillion. And it's not just crypto geeks whose dreams have been shattered, but also ordinary mum and dad investors sucked in by the hype the currency had gone mainstream. However, while many millionaires have become overnight paupers, cryptocurrency's true believers say don't worry, the good times will return.
